(2,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Cream Floor and Wall Tile Code29090 (600x1200mm, Glossy)',70,'Enhance the beauty and functionality of your interiors with our 2x4 feet vitrified glossy floor and wall tiles. Designed to elevate the look of any space, these high-quality ceramic tiles offer a sleek, shiny finish that complements modern aesthetics. The vitrified surface ensures superior durability, stain resistance, and easy maintenance, making them perfect for high-traffic areas such as kitchens, bathrooms, living rooms, and commercial spaces. With their large format size, these tiles create a seamless, contemporary look, reducing grout lines for a smoother finish. Whether for flooring or wall applications, these tiles provide a stylish and long-lasting solution to suit any design preference.','Cream, Red','Ceramic, Contemporary, Glossy, Large Format, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0d8511-2a11-55cb-8270-723117f675/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1657f8-df76-1deb-abc-ab06846a2fd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/30c54e8-2f61-45e-2ef0-d38b515b0405/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4d6727-813e-7f0d-bc85-83f65d83f123/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/66e0aa6-ab0b-5aa3-3a5c-f84cb6ddf72/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ad71cf-c1ac-014-cf3e-b2826e167b6/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ad71cf-c1ac-014-cf3e-b2826e167b6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/cddbbf-3bbd-a87e-612-dd0a0a1531f6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/dc5e8b-6134-4062-e13-5f7680a13ec/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/pub