(3,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Beige Slab Floor and Wall Tile Code29067 (1200x2400mm, Glossy)',189,'Transform your interiors with the elegance of the 4x8 feet marble design slab tile in a glossy finish. This vitrified tile replicates the beauty of natural marble with stunning veining patterns, offering a sophisticated look for both floor and wall applications. The glossy finish adds a high-end sheen, reflecting light to create a bright and spacious ambiance. Ideal for luxurious living rooms, bathrooms, and feature walls, the tile is designed for durability with its vitrified construction, making it resistant to moisture, stains, and heavy wear. Easy to maintain and long-lasting, this marble design slab tile combines classic marble aesthetics with the practical benefits of vitrified tiles, perfect for creating a stylish and resilient space.','Beige, Light','Glossy, Marble, Natural, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/155f8-ae82-4b3a-fd4e-f7fba137702/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1f0460d-de74-0d1c-1441-6cff7cf0c642/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1f0460d-de74-0d1c-1441-6cff7cf0c642/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/20d172d-3526-05-1dad-eba4a51b725/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2d440b-b828-3674-51ed-c44f776cef1f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/307603-a6ac-cf77-5f-715c637ee1a8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4f00bca-3f3-d4c-256-fbf2852e146f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5e26a23-f2d0-f0a2-808a-a43446a640d4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8266470-b2ef-be65-a52-fd82402778e8/600x600.webp, https://corewebim