(4,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Brown Modular Floor and Wall Tile Code35149 (500x500mm, Matt)',101,'The Modular Design Tile brings a perfect balance of style and flexibility to your interiors. Crafted with precision, these tiles feature interlocking patterns that can be arranged in various layouts, allowing endless design possibilities. Ideal for creating unique flooring or accent walls, they blend modern aesthetics with practical durability. Suitable for living rooms, kitchens, bathrooms, and commercial spaces, modular tiles offer easy installation and a timeless, coordinated look. The Modular Design Tile is a versatile and stylish choice for both residential and commercial interiors. Its unique modular pattern allows you to create endless combinations, from symmetrical layouts to creative, statement-making designs. Each tile is crafted with high-quality materials, ensuring durability, stain resistance, and easy maintenance. Perfect for floors, walls, and feature areas, these tiles seamlessly fit together for a cohesive and professional finish. The modular system makes installation quick and precise, while the contemporary patterns elevate any spacebe it modern, industrial, or classic.','Brown','Contemporary, Industrial, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/05cdba4-d50e-1c86-ea80-420fd2c4832/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0738e10-610-d600-44ef-b2fc1c3d4de/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0738e10-610-d600-44ef-b2fc1c3d4de/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0e7d5-054b-078d-ebdb-4737b1e05d2/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2f650ec-d8c4-f8b6-d7c-3d34f886d0/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/60f88c5-636d-1e48-a254-ee243edc5f55/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a375208-5dc1-78b-d5be-346ad20fa055/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d620ae8-4e8c-8ce2-a1c2-20b5e1176d25/600x600.webp','500x500mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-brown-modular-floor-and-wall-tile-code35149-500x500mm-matt'),
(5,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Imported White Oh My Cat Floor and Wall Tile Code32202 (250x250mm, Matt)',594,'Capturing the appearance of a patterned look, our Oh My Cat Vitrified Floor and Wall Tile features a mixed textured finish, making it a great choice for your space. With its impervious, frost-resistant features, this white specialty tile is an ideal selection for both indoor and outdoor residential installations, including kitchens, bathrooms, backsplashes, showers, hallways and fireplace facades. This tile is a perfect choice on its own or paired with other products in the Mytyles. Tile is the better choice for your space.','Mix, Red, White','Patterned, Textured, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2c7fc3-e3b8-31f-8cfc-11580d1a1333/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3d275-50be-a857-454b-17ed6d114b87/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/61da7f2-58d4-7e45-e5e3-cb347b05b/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/61da7f2-58d4-7e45-e5e3-cb347b05b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/63d1d8e-3670-4f3c-8713-e03ddaedfc42/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/681cec-abeb-f717-2262-4dafdd3d38fd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b7d4ba3-cbd-462-bce-d3fec88664/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e00c1da-a245-8118-564d-5e81a0a833ef/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ef70f3d-60cb-6bc3-ae2a-48a437bc7f3/600x600.webp','250x250mm','https://mytyles.com/product/imported-white-oh-my-cat-floor-and-wall-tile-code32202-250x250mm-matt'),
(6,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Cream Digital Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code31010 (500x500mm, Matt)',64,'This 20x20 inch digital parking tile is engineered to withstand heavy traffic, both from vehicles and pedestrians. It features a high-definition, digitally printed surface that allows for intricate, customizable patterns or designs. The tile is typically made from materials like porcelain, ceramic, or high-density composite, which ensures strength, longevity, and resistance to wear and tear.','Cream, Red','Ceramic, Digital, Porcelain, Printed, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0efd1-5b0-4fc6-5cf-ac68322ee2c7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/318c3a2-e0dc-4d67-1f44-a7816fdcbe5c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4452560-ad83-eb6f-5254-fa81fb0c240/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a124e7-08a0-7712-bc-54a5a2d8d75d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b873a7b-a2cd-060-cea2-18f7a04c1637/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b873a7b-a2cd-060-cea2-18f7a04c1637/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d3b0358-b52-e1b5-4b-05e148be87d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e23ec0-6a10-03be-5614-e0756b8174e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/f1ec75c-2835-1ca0-84bd-f44b04856a7/600x600.webp','500x500mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-ivory-digital-parking-floor-and-wall-tile-code31010-500x500mm-matt'),
(7,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Brown Digital Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code36645 (400x400mm, Matt)',85,'The 400x400mm vitrified parking floor and wall tile is specially designed to withstand heavy load, constant movement, and harsh outdoor conditions. Manufactured using high-density vitrification technology, this tile offers excellent strength, low water absorption, and superior resistance to stains, impact, and abrasion. Its compact size ensures better grip and stability, making it ideal for parking areas, driveways, ramps, basements, and utility zones. The durable surface finish provides enhanced slip resistance for safety, while the robust structure ensures long-lasting performance with minimal maintenance. Suitable for both floor and wall applications, this 400x400mm vitrified parking tile combines functionality, reliability, and a clean, structured look for residential and commercial exteriors.','Brown, Red','Digital, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1cac12d-f515-d08d-4e20-f480117e1df0/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1eb8f5-65a0-bf84-1b53-2dfb488fcf/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8308047-b176-7848-e1c-a2cd25351bec/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8aab62-fe6d-efdc-02a-c344fb0d3ed/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c7764ad-786-eb4-08-4c34e6fa7e2/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d0585e3-5234-62b5-b7b5-452612b0b3a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e1560-dfd3-2c8f-382-010b4e17e763/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e1560-dfd3-2c8f-382-010b4e17e763/600x600.webp','400x400mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-brown-digital-parking-floor-and-wall-tile-code36645-400x400mm-matt'),
(8,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Brown Digtal Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code36580 (400x400mm, Matt)',61,'The 400x400mm vitrified parking floor and wall tile is specially designed to withstand heavy load, constant movement, and harsh outdoor conditions. Manufactured using high-density vitrification technology, this tile offers excellent strength, low water absorption, and superior resistance to stains, impact, and abrasion. Its compact size ensures better grip and stability, making it ideal for parking areas, driveways, ramps, basements, and utility zones. The durable surface finish provides enhanced slip resistance for safety, while the robust structure ensures long-lasting performance with minimal maintenance. Suitable for both floor and wall applications, this 400x400mm vitrified parking tile combines functionality, reliability, and a clean, structured look for residential and commercial exteriors.','Brown, Red','Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0bd276b-b3c4-e667-e75c-d2d5a135d477/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/26ed448-361b-b1fa-7350-b3e7e7f3aae/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/45241f-f2ee-c0cf-ff7a-a1b133dfee58/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4e36e32-d82-83f4-6536-8118317dd376/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/516277-31bd-ae1a-e8d-b255dc8ffb1b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/afba2e-1d1e-afbe-823-c2cbf71fd25/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ffd08-f04-c25d-be74-124a68770458/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ffd08-f04-c25d-be74-124a68770458/600x600.webp','400x400mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-brown-digtal-parking-floor-and-wall-tile-code36580-400x400mm-matt'),
(9,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Blue Digital Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code36591 (400x400mm, Matt)',59,'The 400x400mm vitrified floor and wall tile is a versatile and durable solution crafted to enhance both residential and commercial spaces. With its balanced size, it offers the perfect combination of functionality and aesthetics, making it suitable for a wide range of applications. Made from high-quality vitrified, this tile provides excellent strength and long-lasting performance while being easy to maintain. Its smooth yet sturdy surface is resistant to stains, scratches, and moisture, ensuring reliability even in high-traffic areas. The design features a natural stone-inspired texture with subtle variations, adding depth, warmth, and character to any interior or exterior setting. This tile size is ideal for creating seamless layouts that minimize grout lines, giving a cleaner and more spacious appearance. Its versatile design makes it perfect for living rooms, kitchens, bathrooms, balconies, and commercial areas, blending effortlessly with both modern and traditional décor styles. Beyond its durability and visual appeal, the 400x400mm Vitrified tile is also eco-friendly and easy to clean, making it a practical choice for everyday living.','Blue, Red','Digital, Modern, Natural, Traditional, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1216c2-6d41-471-50-a523876516f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/38f0164-cb8-2e38-b65f-53663b6efb1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/40b4a3a-a41f-0186-1a3f-8b651c5ee5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4af11f0-cf06-8d0-1c62-6c6f40f13b1f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/57d81a0-66fc-d38f-325b-258f7dc2aa5f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b3