(10,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Beige Digital Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code36736 (600x600mm, Matt)',84,'The 600x600mm vitrified parking floor and wall tile is specially designed to withstand heavy loads and continuous movement in parking and driveway areas. Manufactured using high-density vitrified material, it offers exceptional strength, high load-bearing capacity, and very low water absorption, ensuring long-term durability in both indoor and outdoor parking spaces. The anti-skid surface provides enhanced grip and safety, even in wet or oily conditions, while the robust finish resists stains, scratches, and tyre marks. Its 600x600mm size allows for uniform installation with a clean, structured appearance, making it suitable for residential parking, commercial garages, basements, and ramps. Easy to maintain and weather-resistant, this tile combines functionality with a neat, professional look.','Beige, Red','Digital, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0c17bc-1723-ab64-76e-8afaaf4703cb/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/21e8f2-fc1e-5f7-7d0b-0d4cff55120/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/412c65-fe16-c6b5-fee-cbde5fb06ea0/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/412c65-fe16-c6b5-fee-cbde5fb06ea0/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/cecf287-0418-cfbe-3aee-8cef3c305aef/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/cf4201-e5b7-aa30-b1f4-d106c3f050c5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d8df1e1-7b6-66df-706a-4122b1aeec/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/f3c253f-7a0-f3c6-3b03-b6eec057a6e/600x600.webp','600x600mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-beige-digital-parking-floor-and-wall-tile-cod