(11,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Brown Digital Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code36598 (400x400mm, Matt)',59,'The 400x400mm vitrified floor and wall tile is a versatile and durable solution crafted to enhance both residential and commercial spaces. With its balanced size, it offers the perfect combination of functionality and aesthetics, making it suitable for a wide range of applications. Made from high-quality vitrified, this tile provides excellent strength and long-lasting performance while being easy to maintain. Its smooth yet sturdy surface is resistant to stains, scratches, and moisture, ensuring reliability even in high-traffic areas. The design features a natural stone-inspired texture with subtle variations, adding depth, warmth, and character to any interior or exterior setting. This tile size is ideal for creating seamless layouts that minimize grout lines, giving a cleaner and more spacious appearance. Its versatile design makes it perfect for living rooms, kitchens, bathrooms, balconies, and commercial areas, blending effortlessly with both modern and traditional décor styles. Beyond its durability and visual appeal, the 400x400mm Vitrified tile is also eco-friendly and easy to clean, making it a practical choice for everyday living.','Brown, Red','Digital, Modern, Natural, Traditional, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3383f51-bcbc-f516-ad0f-3762e86cea1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7d2f32-62b4-3f83-6bdf-526dbff077b4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/84ee204-668-1b03-f872-e42506a77e1c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/bc4e567-521-856-3a13-1f04c5f6084/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/dcc2c3-2f1a-71d-60c0-80454d7d25a/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/ima