(41,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code23045 (300x300mm, Metallic)',355,'A medley of textures and warm colours come together in this stunning 12 x 18 inch Moroccan wall and floor tile by MyTyles to give your surfaces a clandestine rustic fervour. Riddled with duotone finishes including the vivid marbled tonal undulations and a rare glimmer, the body of this extraordinarily sturdy ceramic tile is embellished with a repetitive floral pattern, the marbled patterns on the colour palette have an equally distinguished duotone finishes. The dramatic nature of the textures and golden hints all along the body imparts a delightful touch. Sharp looks aided by the gentle sheen from the satin matte glaze, this ceramic wall and floor tile provides breathtaking finishes including wall facade remodels and expansive flooring to your residential and commercial with zero inhibitions around technical glitches or aesthetic hesitations. Designed to thrive in with a sturdy build, exceptional resistance and a stunning sense of style, this Moroccan tile is a dream to maintain and style.','Gold, Light, Metallic','Ceramic, Floral, Marble, Matte, Rustic, Satin, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/18368b4-7f-41d-ceb6-418b327f3ccb/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1f273e4-4fa-21c4-848-fdbcbf48cc57/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/53e36e8-d832-142e-5d74-da67c4b62f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/53e66a2-a0cc-0086-b15-2056f412d5a5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5df0e86-7aaf-7aaf-dd5e-87b508de3cb/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5df0e86-7aaf-7aaf-dd5e-87b508de3cb/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/67c0f6-6c05-3085-5568-3d7808141/60