(48,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Wooden Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Brown Wooden Floor and Wall Tile Code36988 (600x1200mm, Matt)',75,'The 600x1200mm vitrified wooden floor and wall tile beautifully combines the natural warmth of wood with the strength and durability of vitrified tiles, making it an excellent choice for contemporary and classic interiors alike. Its large rectangular format reduces grout lines, creating a smooth, continuous surface that enhances the sense of space while delivering an authentic wood-plank appearance. The realistic grain patterns and tonal variations replicate the charm of natural timber, adding warmth and character without the maintenance concerns of real wood. Manufactured using advanced vitrification technology, this tile offers high durability, low water absorption, and strong resistance to stains, scratches, and moisture, making it suitable for both floors and walls. Unlike natural wood, it does not warp, fade, or require polishing, ensuring long-lasting performance even in high-traffic areas. Ideal for living rooms, bedrooms, kitchens, bathrooms, balconies, offices, and commercial spaces, the 600x1200mm vitrified wooden tile blends aesthetic elegance with practical functionality, delivering a timeless, nature-inspired look with modern reliability.','Brown, Red','Contemporary, Modern, Natural, Plank, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0beeee1-1d07-80c-7ddb-33350dfa5e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/37576d4-383b-0617-2a0-de5c1ce500a/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/37576d4-383b-0617-2a0-de5c1ce500a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4213dcb-34e8-e6-000-7f56f5d6aa/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4b07a76-1540-02aa-17f-3f47dba870f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/pr