(53,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Wooden Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Tile Code20359 (600x600mm, Matt)',61,'With distressed and dry brushstroke tones, this collection of 2 x 2 feet vitrified wall and floor tiles by MyTyles offers a sense of warmth to your decor. Decorated with swirls and grains mimicking the feel of authentic wooden planks in a slab format, this wood finished wall and floor tile is laced with exquisite blends. The thick graining is accompanied by vivid knots whereas the bold textures render a sophisticated feel. Feathering and weathering aside, the top notch digital printing on these large format vitrified tiles renders the viewer beguiled with the spectacular attention to detail whereas the sturdy build brings hardwearing sturdiness to the mix. Forging a gateway between organic aesthetics and advancements in digital printing technology, this collection of double fired vitrified tiles are available in two endearing variants: dark (with hickory accents on a warm brown) and light (decadent coffee colored knots on desert brown base glaze). Rectified edges and convenient sizing aside, these vitrified wall and floor tiles are bewildering and aweworthy.','Brown, Dark, Light, Mix, Red','Cement, Digital, Distressed, Large Format, Plank, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6d200f-16f4-ef06-07bd-83482ee1454e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8f2fff4-bb5-0a50-c1-ccec01830d7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ba40316-c713-0145-6a6-2bc2864fb11/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/bedf75c-3e2-bbb1-b0ca-cf565d031/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/cf44564-ba77-e36-ac73-55163a21c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e48f370-86ba-4eb5-f714-8ec17d6544a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.