(60,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Wooden Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Brown Wooden Floor and Wall Tile Code35961 (200x1200mm, Matt)',88,'A wood-look tile should feel authentic while staying tough enough for real life. This brown wooden vitrified tile is made in a 200x1200 mm plank size that creates a clean, linear finish across floors and walls. Tile Code 35961 provides a dense vitrified body that supports long-term durability with low water absorption. The matt finish keeps the surface calm and helps the wood grain detailing look more natural. It also reduces visible streaks, which is useful in homes with regular movement. The brown tone leans warm and works well with cream walls, soft greys, brushed metal fittings, and earthy decor. You get the comfort of a timber aesthetic without worrying about swelling, staining, or surface polishing. This tile is suitable for floors in bedrooms, lounges, and dining areas, and it also works on walls as cladding for feature elevations. The long plank format reduces grout breaks and creates a more continuous look. For best results, plan the layout direction to match the rooms longest visual line.','Brown, Cream, Grey, Red','Natural, Plank, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/118013a-5b04-0bf2-5ea6-4045f7bf4478/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/118013a-5b04-0bf2-5ea6-4045f7bf4478/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/36238c-d2e1-3d8b-5e1f-458e46e4a53a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/45ec372-0e-6532-8e50-271881e3a5b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/665035-03b4-bab4-687a-d3da4b3654f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/888570-7757-52-e118-7670566c14f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8e06245-f7dc-ad