(73,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Wooden Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Brown Wooden Floor and Wall Tile Code35962 (200x1200mm, Matt)',88,'Wood-styled interiors feel warmer when you use a plank-format tile that also handles daily wear. This brown wooden vitrified tile comes in a 200x1200 mm size, giving you long, continuous lines that mimic real flooring planks. It is listed as Tile Code 35962 and is manufactured using vitrified technology, which creates a dense body with low water absorption and strong surface stability. The matt finish keeps reflections controlled and gives the surface a natural look that suits both daylight and warm indoor lighting. The brown tone carries a timber-inspired character that pairs well with beige walls, charcoal accents, black fixtures, and soft textiles. Unlike natural wood, this tile does not swell, peel, or demand polishing. Use it on floors for an organised plank layout or extend it onto walls for a coordinated finish. It works well in living rooms, bedrooms, kitchens, corridors, and commercial interiors where wood style is wanted without fragile maintenance routines.','Beige, Black, Brown, Charcoal, Light, Red','Natural, Plank, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2be6283-55d6-cff-4f03-3f26c5726bac/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5dffa8-e650-a58-450-0d54a0be3158/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/77acba4-b17b-a51e-6a7d-074f8582623/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7c68130-eeaa-828a-c03-f1d422e6c7d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/887750-081c-1f-744c-42dfebcddd7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8e03b10-3c78-6e47-181-507cf4d6fdc4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8f817b2-2bba-0bf6-8ac-3b12fa86c8