(75,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Wooden Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Wooden Tile Code20346 (600x600mm, Matt)',68,'This 2 x 2 feet wooden vitrified wall and floor tile by MyTyles strikes the right balance between organic tones, printed and embossed textures and hyperealistic display of contemporary touches. Engaging with dark wooden tones and complete with knots, swirls and gradients to add ample visual depth, the harmonious blends of ashy grays and mahogany adds a sense of vivid, passionate movement with its dark and sultry aesthetic to amplify the delectable touch of this wood finished vitrified tile. Designed to instill an instant influx of sophistication into any space, use this large format wooden wall and floor tile to bring modernist touch your wall and floor facades including kitchen, bedroom, bathroom, everyday living areas, and more, whether used in residential or commercial properties. Establishing a serene continuity, this large format vitrified tile delivers a swift convenient transformation while keeping everyday wear and tear at bay and reducing wear and tear to the bare minimum. Designed to instill an instant influx of sophistication into any space, use this large format wooden wall and floor tile to bring modernist touch your wall and floor facades including kitchen, bedroom, bathroom, everyday living areas, and more, whether used in residential or commercial properties. Establishing a serene continuity, this large format vitrified tile delivers a swift convenient transformation while keeping everyday wear and tear at bay and reducing wear and tear to the bare minimum.','Dark, Gray, Red','Contemporary, Large Format, Modern, Printed, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/03cac3f-aa11-c4fc-105-477dbbb8de/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1085e16-c3c5-263f-4722-10ab81b655/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/25d03a-64