(76,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Wooden Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Brown Wooden Floor and Wall Tile Code35963 (200x1200mm, Matt)',88,'This 200x1200mm vitrified wooden floor and wall tile brings the warmth of natural timber together with the strength of vitrified technology, creating a perfect blend of beauty and durability. Designed with high-definition digital printing, each plank captures realistic wood grains, knots, and subtle tonal variations, giving it the authentic charm of hardwood flooring without the maintenance challenges. The elongated plank format enhances visual continuity, making rooms appear wider and more elegant. Crafted with low water absorption and superior surface strength, this tile is ideal for homes and commercial spaces, delivering long-lasting performance in living rooms, bedrooms, balconies, corridors, and feature walls. Its slip-resistant, stain-proof, and scratch-resistant properties ensure an easy-to-maintain surface that stays pristine over time. Perfect for creating warm, modern, and nature-inspired interiors, this vitrified wooden tile adds timeless sophistication to any environment.','Brown, Red','Digital, Modern, Natural, Plank, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/18873-1487-5cd-a5fe-34db511326d5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1cedb23-4811-d11a-b684-4ffb283a08/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/216b1ef-f85f-802-6d4c-211a36f550/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3062124-5438-f8c-3c-83517e61780/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3d020c-44b0-edd-278-daeeba20cc0/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/51ab7-2a82-025b-a804-74780d7a4a8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/543ad5b-62b8-a616-6ca-4e684c3c617c/1