(84,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Wooden Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Gray Wooden Floor and Wall Tile Code36996 (600x1200mm, Matt)',75,'The 600x1200mm vitrified wooden floor and wall tile beautifully captures the warmth and natural charm of real wood while offering the strength and durability of vitrified tiles. Designed with realistic wood grain textures and tonal variations, it delivers an authentic timber look without the issues of warping, moisture damage, or heavy maintenance. Manufactured using advanced vitrification technology, the tile has a dense, non-porous body that ensures excellent resistance to water, stains, scratches, and daily wear. Its large-format 600x1200mm size creates a seamless, elegant finish with fewer grout lines, making spaces look expansive and well-defined. Suitable for both floor and wall applications, this wooden-look vitrified tile is ideal for living rooms, bedrooms, kitchens, bathrooms, feature walls, and commercial interiors. Blending natural aesthetics with modern performance, it complements contemporary, rustic, and minimalist design styles while providing long-lasting beauty and easy maintenance.','Gray, Red','Contemporary, Minimalist, Modern, Natural, Rustic, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3b355c7-f2ae-6886-551c-b03083aaac4f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3c0d8-1eb-7abd-e01-0d5d5646413/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5be36f-7f1e-7466-0f2f-10bdb2440820/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/71af71-6b1-5ab3-1f23-c41f75a4db22/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/bff23f-4eab-0f3a-c67f-1af2da08662/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/bff23f-4eab-0f3a-c67f-1af2da08662/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/im