(85,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Wooden Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Gray Wooden Floor and Wall Tile Code32817 (80x450mm, Matt)',176,'The 80x450mm Vitrified Wooden Floor and Wall Tile combines the timeless beauty of wood with the durability and ease of ceramic tiles. Designed to mimic the natural elegance of wooden planks, this vitrified tile offers a warm, organic aesthetic without the maintenance hassles of real wood. Perfect for both floor and wall installations, it is ideal for creating a rustic or contemporary look in any space, whether residential or commercial. Thanks to its vitrified finish, this tile is highly resistant to moisture, stains, and scratches, making it suitable for high-traffic areas and even wet environments like bathrooms and kitchens. The long, slim format provides a sleek, modern appearance, whether used to create a seamless wooden floor or an eye-catching wall feature.','Gray','Ceramic, Contemporary, Modern, Natural, Plank, Rustic, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2b12e38-843f-8a08-5f3f-042b038cb48/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2b1fff-44c1-56df-e3a-171f5436460/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2d71cc-3055-254f-ff7e-035ca7cc6d0c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/65c5c86-5b66-5fb-c68-c58f643405/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/71cfe81-0337-f2bb-f42e-d2def7b7e34/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7fc2a58-c3f-fc01-b4b-82f500a801b/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7fc2a58-c3f-fc01-b4b-82f500a801b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/aefc40-dce3-c0de-c281-a172516cb64c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b82