46-bc6-a8-6d27a5287b28/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/803b51c-6846-bc6-a8-6d27a5287b28/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a1b7263-73e-ac8-2e2e-aa647326dba/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/cc0bf2-52e8-d885-17e3-3a7f80d447/600x600.webp','600x1200mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-beige-floor-and-wall-tile-code37412-600x1200mm-carving-matt'),
(99,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Marble Vitrified Tiles','Full Body Vitrified Gray Slab Floor and Wall Tile Code33477 (800x2400mm, Matt)',180,'Decorated with a soft Arabescato like exterior, the looks of this collection of 2.5 x 8 feet vitrified wall and floor tile by MyTyles draws you in from the first glance. Soft, matt grays pave the way for whites and creamy ivory against an alluring white backdrop to replicate the nuanced authenticity of split face finishes. The sturdy build coupled with the organic aesthetic makes this collection of double fired vitrified slab compatible with a host of decor styles, a range of conversation starting centerpieces while making your spaces look well-ventilated. The stunning looks and the spectacular glaze work are consistent across both the variations in thick collection of this vitrified wall and floor slabs. Encouraging elegance and upscale looks at the fraction of the price of natural stones, the performance of these large format vitrified tiles makes it a suitable choice amongst residential and commercial properties alike.','Cream, Gray, Ivory, Red, White','Full Body, Large Format, Natural, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/28e6021-3c6-b818-a082-a8411f2d1aec/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/28e6021-3c6-b818-a082-a8411f2d1aec/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/30c8e33-f47c-7f46-17a8-6ed3bbe2286e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4ef6c0-0043-20d2-266c-40ce8c26b12/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5a0436-4b2d-0b65-e02-1564381da7ae/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/65eef2-cc2c-8e17-22fd-7da7dfe4775/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6cbaca-ee8f-ae60-504-8f476e6d0e5c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/773502e-7d3b-826-d368-ff53bc0ffee/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7fd42-7acf-f37b-d857-4f3800012c8c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/85e4c8-1cd-7336-151f-d3e4637a4fa/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c00c42-3eee-f0e3-a30-30feab671a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ea63815-10c-e7ae-c205-a40ecc1353e0/600x600.webp','800x2400mm','https://mytyles.com/product/full-body-vitrified-gray-slab-floor-and-wall-tile-code33477-800x2400mm-matt'),
(100,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Marble Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified White Slab Floor and Wall Tile Code22047 (790x3000x15mm, Matt)',297,'Introduce timeless elegance to your interiors with this 2.5x10 feet marble-look slab tile featuring a sophisticated matte finish. The large slab format reduces grout lines, creating a smooth, expansive look that enhances the natural marble effect. The matte finish adds a subtle, understated elegance, perfect for contemporary and classic designs alike. Ideal for use on walls, floors, or countertops, this tile combines the beauty of marble with the durability of tile, making it a versatile choice for residential and commercial spaces.','Red, White','Contemporary, Marble, Matte, Natural, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1163f72-1ded-1a4-b4a8-0a11b772c27/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/15e55b-650-4b5-f002-874e4f8e1cd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2cf614-8cde-a6f3-0162-8baeef4b86b3/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2cf614-8cde-a6f3-0162-8baeef4b86b3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/30ae075-8d63-7e70-ca4-ade7b61e3c2/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/31fd6d-e546-b3fd-32e6-2f7b4337ce26/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/41ad02b-00f-dcfc-555f-e1a7a77d6ae/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4ef5828-e6e1-6ba8-7ff-a46aa5c14287/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5ea2afe-6af-5dca-666e-7e2f5a50e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/62f831-3f06-a40-c673-463c841e3bd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/63cc28e-0