(103,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Marble Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Mint Green Textured Wall Tile Code34110 (600x1200mm, Matt)',84,'The 600x1200mm vitrified textured wall tile features a modern mosaic-inspired design with a subtle blend of warm brown, beige, and cream tones set against a soft neutral base. Its textured surface adds depth and character, creating an eye-catching visual appeal while maintaining a natural and earthy aesthetic. Crafted with high-quality vitrified material, this tile offers excellent durability, stain resistance, and low maintenance, making it ideal for accent walls, living rooms, bathrooms, and commercial spaces. The large-format size ensures minimal grout lines and a seamless finish, bringing elegance and contemporary charm to any interior décor.','Beige, Brown, Cream, Green, Red','Contemporary, Modern, Mosaic, Natural, Textured, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/124070-5346-3def-faeb-08b3e6312e84/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1652ffc-fe57-2374-10ad-d5f8e76bf4c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5247a3-8816-35-e420-226a34b467b3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e77fb-fdd5-ec46-cf46-c1ab37f56e8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ed305bb-d140-c4ef-61ec-d3f00ddb56d/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ed305bb-d140-c4ef-61ec-d3f00ddb56d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/eff46e-636-c00c-a525-aedf287736/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/f3f3a8f-45b-cbaa-af50-ec2c6a40a653/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/fcbc0b2-be37-7f0-5106-86bf0dcab46/600x600.webp','600x1200mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-mint-green-textured-wall-tile-code34110-600x1200mm-matt'),
(104,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Marble Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Gray Slab Floor and Wall Tile Code37287 (1200x1800mm, Glossy)',98,'Make a bold design statement with our 4x6 ft Vitrified Glossy Finish Floor and Wall Tile, where minimalist style meets maximum impact. This large-format vitrified tile is engineered for strength, durability, and visual appeal, making it the perfect choice for contemporary spaces that demand elegance with functionality. The Glossy finish offers a natural, non-reflective surface with a soft texture that adds depth and warmth to interiors. It provides excellent slip resistance, making it ideal for high-traffic areas, bathrooms, kitchens, and open living spaces. With fewer grout lines due to its impressive 4x6 ft size, it creates a seamless, expansive look that enhances both residential and commercial interiors. Crafted using advanced vitrification technology, the tile is resistant to stains, moisture, and scratches, ensuring long-lasting beauty and low maintenance.','Gray, Red','Contemporary, Glossy, Minimalist, Natural, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0c3bdd-33b4-da46-baa1-8d30dc7462c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/158ec-bffa-43b6-f546-db25dd4e6f4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2858cfa-5c8-3be1-6c26-55a3fcba7a66/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2fe6c4d-7e0f-a04-c057-53e12b523c8/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2fe6c4d-7e0f-a04-c057-53e12b523c8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/34f07eb-a34-0b4c-657a-d1e341b7c88b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4fcc0cb-4230-53c8-f64-f30e62623b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6cde23c-8544-8283-6dec-5