(105,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Marble Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Black Floor and Wall Tile Code37296 (1200x1800mm, Matt)',130,'The 4x6 feet vitrified floor and wall tile with matt finish is designed to deliver a sophisticated, contemporary look with a strong focus on practicality and elegance. Its expansive large-format size minimizes grout lines, creating a seamless, continuous surface that enhances spatial flow and gives interiors a clean, uncluttered appearance. The matt finish offers a soft, natural texture that reduces glare and provides a refined, understated aesthetic. Manufactured using advanced vitrification technology, this tile ensures high strength, low porosity, and excellent resistance to moisture, stains, and scratches. The matt surface adds better slip resistance compared to glossy tiles, making it a reliable choice for both dry and slightly wet areas. Its durable structure makes it suitable for high-traffic zones while maintaining its original look over time. Ideal for floors and walls, this tile fits effortlessly into living rooms, bedrooms, kitchens, bathrooms, corridors, commercial spaces, offices, and hospitality environments.','Black, Light, Red','Contemporary, Glossy, Natural, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/042abbc-71e-34a6-08-62bd82ef03b7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/04486c4-4456-58ff-455e-f7f153c48edf/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1b8d036-1161-4f60-12ff-ad073630de/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1f0b4-fdb-85a-10a1-c32481f486a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/21ff0f-e763-66f2-825-205e62b10d6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/240b4f-026f-fce6-32-2eaa1ef3b87/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3585abc-1581-ac-470-a265ba03ca03/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3a40230-e241-23e-ff04-71c48c363c3c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4f5417d-dedc-5523-50ae-6268b1442102/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7a6dd3-72ea-255-2246-73e66cbbe71d/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7a6dd3-72ea-255-2246-73e66cbbe71d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ea38cdf-abb-4542-4076-70534525d65/600x600.webp','1200x1800mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-black-floor-and-wall-tile-code37296-1200x1800mm-matt'),
(106,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Marble Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified White 15mm Slab Floor and Wall Tile Code37104 (1200x1800mm, Matt)',155,'The Vitrified 15mm Slab Floor and Wall Tile is designed to deliver superior strength, refined aesthetics, and long-lasting performance for both residential and commercial spaces. Manufactured using high-density vitrified technology with a solid 15mm thickness, this slab tile offers exceptional durability, load-bearing capacity, and resistance to impact, making it ideal for high-traffic areas. Its large slab format creates a seamless, expansive look with minimal grout lines, enhancing the overall visual appeal of floors and walls. The smooth, premium surface finish adds a touch of sophistication while being resistant to stains, scratches, moisture, and daily wear. Easy to clean and maintain, this tile ensures a hygienic and long-lasting surface. Suitable for living rooms, bedrooms, kitchens, bathrooms, feature walls, lobbies, and commercial interiors, the Vitrified 15mm Slab Tile brings together modern elegance, structural strength, and versatile design for contemporary architectural spaces.','Red, White','Contemporary, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0a0c8-c0ab-76d-361d-3307110c5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0c182ae-375b-2b4-d52d-7c4edba7532/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0c182ae-375b-2b4-d52d-7c4edba7532/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2880d8f-3fd3-a531-a780-a0ed1a082b82/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2b8120-cb8-110-8207-10ce55174046/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3d0dddf-8de5-6452-f361-5d3aff2b8a4c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/51f1adb-bed1-b1a-eefe-c7f85