(131,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / 3D Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Elevation Tile Code8073 (300x600mm, Matt)',90,'This collection of organic and geometric 2 x 1 feet vitrified elevation wall tiles by MyTyles relies on encaustic patterns and three dimensional prints to add immaculate depth and dimension to your exteriors. These double fired vitrified tile sports a repetitive print with neatly arranged patterns with the finesse of finer details to add to the geometric design. Equipped to give any surface the authentic look and feel, both the ivory and nero variants in this collection of elevation wall tiles are laced with the subtle sheen of satin matte glaze for maximum longevity. Whether used to refashion a cozy nook in the balcony, elevate exteriors of your properties or design offbeat semi-outdoor nooks including passageways, parking areas, garages, stairways, and other utilitarian areas in and around the house, this vitrified elevation tile delivers pure excellence. With a large format design, rectified edges and superlative shine, these elevation tiles make for an ageless companion to your remodels.','Ivory, Red','Encaustic, Geometric, Large Format, Matte, Satin, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1c8aba2-300f-aa2a-da47-b7b14b0651fd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2ab5fe5-c37e-6b3-8860-3b284d60cc5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5187f0d-dcff-e6e-1f24-1a3bcd52cc/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5187f0d-dcff-e6e-1f24-1a3bcd52cc/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/55d176-f1c-bbf1-4fb7-ca86bedb0b6d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5b7ec2a-035a-212-570e-3cedd76f8d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8314265-65bc-e180-1a8-e8ba7