(132,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / 3D Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Elevation Tile Code19687 (300x600mm, Matt)',75,'Set your walls free and let them breathe with the Berlin collection from MyTyles. A heavenly marriage of stone cladding aesthetics in a vitrified elevation wall tile format, this collection brings forth groundbreaking advancements in digital printing and combines it with toxin-free and allergen-free raw materials. The impeccable attention to detail in the form of textural undulations and feathered strokes crafts a realistic, dated touch whereas the gradients present a fine interplay of light and shadows. Available in two colours, the brown variation is a hearty mix of bright, warm earthy tones whereas the black variation uses a mix of cool-toned greys and blues with a touch of beige to attain the tinge of warmth. Best suited for outdoor, indoor, and semi-outdoor home remodelling projects. This elevation wall tile lends a gentle magnificent sheen that turns heads and garners compliments. Easy to install and low on maintenance and upkeep, this vitrified wall tile sets the tone for any space irrespective of the decor style.','Beige, Black, Blue, Brown, Grey, Light, Mix, Red','Cement, Digital, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/106757c-c48e-413-65df-c56ae3db50d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5b3433-a0c8-d8b6-c22d-c024a8405b5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5cba852-0a3d-d80d-a2a-30f4f2820571/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5dbe281-dc38-ecdf-04c2-7effbb677fb/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5dbe281-dc38-ecdf-04c2-7effbb677fb/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8b81e8-e755-f6c8-cc61-761037737f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/prod