(133,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / 3D Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code4456 (300x300mm, Matt)',95,'A modern rendition of hydraulic cement tiles and encaustic motifs, this 12 x 12 inch Moroccan wall and floor tile by MyTyles radiates with the new found glow of ethnic style. Simulating the look and feel of fluid encaustic motifs with Moroccan motifs all over, these vitrified tile initiates a instant flutter of versatility and sophistication throughout your spaces. Available in two variations, purple and chantilly, both the variations of these double fired vitrified tiles facilitate and instant upleveling for an artisanal finish. A desirable choice for both indoor floor and wall remodels in indoor and semi-outdoor settings, use this vitrified wall and floor tile to revamp your residential and commercial properties with its sense of effortlessness. With a charming design, the sizable design and rectified edges and the subtle sheen of the satin matte glaze on this large format Moroccan tile ensures swift transformations for a quick influx of elegance without the added hassles in maintenance and upkeep.','Purple, Red','Cement, Encaustic, Large Format, Matte, Modern, Satin, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1627502-77a3-4f4-565-4364ef541418/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2f3ad8-038e-bdd7-5f7-cfc3a36e6362/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/32bbc8-cf1-1c0-157d-e78c611feb/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a0086cb-efac-6c1e-fde-772814555c2/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a0086cb-efac-6c1e-fde-772814555c2/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b6dff34-1b77-2af-d85-e2cff8f616/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b8c21d2-5b4-44a7-