(148,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Granite Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified GVT Slab Tile Code9712 (600x1200mm, Glossy)',50,'Melding ethnic sensibilities with an impeccable sense of style, this 2 x 4 feet vitrified wall and floor tiles by MyTyles is a curious mix of veins, rivulets, smears and fusion at its best. With intersecting, split face textures native to exclusive marbled and a vibrant contrast, these double fired vitrified tiles generate tremendous amounts of grace with the liberal use of neutral hues and warm tones. Available in numerous variants, each variant pairs the design with a sleek sheen to give your surfaces a subtle but undeniable depth and dimension that echoes throughout your decor. Resilient and reliable because of its efficacious make and build, these vitrified wall and floor slabs can be used to design outstanding indoor and semi-outdoor spaces in and around the house. A superlative blend of colors, patterns, and more, these vitrified slabs tolerates the harshest of circumstance with effortless ease and grace thereby leaving you with a startling eye for details.','Mix, Red, Vibrant','Glossy, Marble, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/13ff57c-42b1-840e-0737-bffcfa65430d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/17b2a7-6a03-8437-402-aca717a530fd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/18418-ea0b-c842-517d-c5a5edba4321/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3888bf0-4084-e7c-4c5d-fc68df1c80f3/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3888bf0-4084-e7c-4c5d-fc68df1c80f3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/51f4bdb-ea7e-540-f4c6-a6fdeddca0b6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b40ce-efb6-5e-ae6b-8dddd336d080/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.my