(151,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Granite Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Cream Slab Floor and Wall Tile Code25873 (790x3000x15mm, Glossy)',263,'Upgrade your interiors with this premium 2.5x10 feet slab tile, offering the timeless elegance of marble in a durable tile format. The high-gloss finish enhances the natural stone look, creating a luxurious and polished appearance perfect for modern and classic spaces alike. Ideal for large-scale projects, this tile is suitable for walls, floors, and countertops in residential and commercial settings. Enjoy the beauty of marble without the maintenance, with a finish thats easy to clean and long-lasting. Create a stunning visual impact with this 2.5x10 feet marble-look slab tile. Designed to emulate the elegance of natural marble, the tile boasts a glossy finish that enhances its luxurious aesthetic. The large format minimizes grout lines, offering a seamless and expansive look, making it perfect for both contemporary and classic interiors. Ideal for floors, walls, and countertops, this tile provides the sophisticated beauty of marble with the durability, ease of maintenance, and longevity of ceramic or porcelain.','Cream','Ceramic, Contemporary, Glossy, Large Format, Marble, Modern, Natural, Polished, Porcelain, Stone Look, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/260ed70-6132-c260-0da8-4733c78fe05/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/27bf70a-b8e-c302-442e-e2d7f5148a1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2afe4da-1864-6a36-15f-80136bd886e0/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7f3145b-fca3-6b0d-bd06-cda42f3843ed/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/85abe7-1a67-acc-6de-e67d4f147b8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8b4eb2b-442c-cd06-73ad-e222f45bc33/600x600.we