(167,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Moroccan Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code23027 (300x300mm, Matt)',230,'Deliver the soothing touch of ethnic patterns and delicate patterns to your home with this 12 x 12 inch Moroccan wall and floor tile by MyTyles. Supporting a 4 x 4 mosaic grid layout with clean and refreshing loops, arcs, and imagery, the sturdy body of this double fired vitrified tile add a dose of modern minimalism to your decor. Featuring a mix of symmetrical detailing on a crisp white base glaze, the minimal elemental essence of this ceramic tile blends well with any space while giving it a whiff of the characteristic contrast, detailing, and more. Suitable for indoor and semi-outdoor wall and floor accents in the kitchen, bathroom, showers, hallways, powder rooms, and other residential and small commercial properties, this ceramic wall and floor tile capitalises on its versatility, durability and sturdiness to leave you with a spectacular, never seen before finesse. Equipped with a sizeable design and the subtle sheen from satin matte glaze for maximum utilitarian features, use this large formar Moroccan tile for a delectable blend of convenience and performance.','Mix, Red, White','Ceramic, Matte, Modern, Mosaic, Satin, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/06b02-405a-ca72-187-1387c50d16f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0a77c83-758a-fa87-ec3b-cfefdbdbca83/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0f1b14-f21f-14-d284-8718e5258233/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/110bc6-ebbf-0b28-b6d5-e440f28a57dd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/168768-a1-027b-ec82-346b31673b07/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/168768-a1-027b-ec82-346b31673b07/600x600.webp, https://corewebimag