(172,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Moroccan Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code23039 (300x300mm, Metallic)',355,'Displaying the simplicity of Tastir and its geometric essence, this collection of 12 x 12 inch Moroccan wall and floor tiles by MyTyles creates a remarkable first impression. The smart use of grains and speckles ensure maximum contrast, making small areas look larger and sizeable areas look cohesively cozy and well put together. With a a simplistic pattern and a medley of charming contrasting hues, this collection of double fired vitrified tiles do not overpower any other elements of the decor. The blue variation combines teal with prussian blue whereas the red variant combines olive with reddish sienna tones; both highlighted with golden accents all over. Use this vitrified wall and floor tile to design exquisite installations in the kitchen, bathroom, mudrooms, front porches, living rooms, balconies or bedrooms either as an accent or as a full blown repetitive body. With a sizeable design, rectified edges, and the subtle sheen from the satin matte glaze, this Moroccan tile displays a sense of effortlessness and timelessness that illuminates your entire space without any overwhelm.','Blue, Gold, Light, Metallic, Olive, Red, Teal','Geometric, Matte, Satin, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0602b06-3cba-a3c7-5344-4b5553a27fb2/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/18d05d3-11f3-b32-161f-bc8ae671d278/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1ee3e5e-2d6d-76fe-215d-6b148ffd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2bb81dc-58c0-f1a-144b-6dd4ade3d8e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2c6ce-ec04-a3c-b2ed-d30cada4f3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5134484-733-6c15-0e-f60f7d0c5751/1