(178,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Moroccan Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code4460 (300x300mm, Matt)',95,'Equipped with the modernity of encaustic patterns, this collection of 12 x 12 inch Moroccan wall and floor tiles by MyTyles sets a strong interlude to your designs. Sporting a variety of floral motifs enclosed within a charming quatrefoil frame in charcoal hues with ornamental details and motifs along the corners, this vitrified tile replicate the look and feel of hydraulic cement tiles. Both the ash grey and bluish grey variants in this collection of double fired vitrified tiles forge breathtaking installation to further enhance the depth and dimension. A befitting feat for a wide variety of indoor and semi-outdoor remodels, use these vitrified wall and floor tiles to craft stylish, end-to-end transformations in the kitchen, bathroom, bedroom, everyday living areas, powder rooms, lounges, mudrooms, and other nooks and crannies without any inhibitions. Resisting moisture, chips, cracks and everyday wear and tear, these Moroccan tiles opens up new avenues for swift transformations with its inherent ease and grace.','Charcoal, Grey, Red','Cement, Encaustic, Floral, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2fde0d6-43f4-8814-12c2-c21e35c53c70/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3ef84bd-1d1c-2c5f-b752-08de0b060fa/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/415ee12-fcbe-d201-acbd-d0e1722b507/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/531d550-d2b-a3d6-cc77-68b6a6efa4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/55db004-ce45-6802-f3aa-20a3245b050e/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/55db004-ce45-6802-f3aa-20a3245b050e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/image