(203,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Moroccan Vitrified Tiles','Imported Moroccan Tile Code2084 (200x200mm, Metallic)',559,'With numerous rustic embellishment, this collection of 8 x 8 inch imported Moroccan wall tiles by MyTyles is both traditional and contemporary in equal proportions. Each Moroccan tile features an ethereal combination of assorted patterns to create captivating surfaces and uplifts any space it inhabits with the faux distressing along the body. Available in four variants, sienna, teal, lead and taupe, each variant is a mesmerizing blend of four unique designs in each boxset for a curated, handpicked and crafted visual appeal. The artisanal feel from the smeared, bleeding edges and lines on the design as well as the subtle sheen from the satin matte glaze on these imported ceramic tiles only amplify the functional utilitarianism of these imported ceramic tiles. A timeless addition to any space, these ceramic tiles display impressive aesthetic sensibility and exceptional durability.','Metallic, Red, Teal','Ceramic, Contemporary, Matte, Rustic, Satin, Traditional','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/05ebffe-74d8-87ad-c3bd-c7628c020d71/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/14102-b77-4060-18de-f644b74d64e1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1c444de-e383-2c72-d02a-d0c3d6646b66/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/247f43-eeac-337-aca3-abf1e63a5b6a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6d562b0-fb7a-0817-2f03-d8e3ea7df0b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/cb35d61-0eb5-241-8beb-61ed5002e8c/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/cb35d61-0eb5-241-8beb-61ed5002e8c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ee63