(205,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Onyx Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Cream Slab Floor and Wall Tile Code35083 (1200x2400mm, Glossy)',225,'The 4x8 feet marble design slab tile in a matte finish combines the luxurious look of natural marble with the durability and practicality of modern tile. Perfect for both floor and wall applications, this large-format tile minimizes grout lines, offering a seamless and sophisticated appearance. The matte finish provides a soft, non-reflective surface that enhances the natural stone look while reducing glare, making it ideal for creating a serene and elegant atmosphere. Designed for both residential and commercial spaces, these tiles are made from high-quality materials, ensuring they are moisture-resistant, durable, and easy to maintain. Whether used in living areas, bathrooms, or hallways, the marble design brings a timeless beauty that elevates any room. Experience timeless luxury with this stunning 4x8 ft marble tile. Crafted from premium natural marble, it showcases exquisite veining and a smooth polished finish, making it perfect for creating spacious, elegant floors or accent walls. Ideal for both residential and commercial interiors, this large-format tile adds a sense of grandeur and sophistication to any space.','Cream, Red','Glossy, Marble, Matte, Modern, Natural, Polished, Stone Look, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1ee18ec-0cd-cc36-7768-fa0c2f11edef/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/22fbad-81a7-30f7-b871-3f7d1b7ae7f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4b1b1a8-6640-f346-136-1220c468fb3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/632e5-b877-b7ca-b25f-50b8c0ff41/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/757351b-e1be-0468-a2cf-f8ada436044/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/