(209,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Onyx Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified White Floor and Wall Tile Code34104 (600x1200mm, Glossy)',73,'A 2x4 feet vitrified floor and wall tile is a large-sized ceramic tile made using the vitrification process, which involves firing the tile at high temperatures to make it dense, durable, and non-porous. The tile is typically used for both floor and wall applications in various residential, commercial, or industrial spaces. These tiles are highly durable and can withstand heavy foot traffic, making them suitable for both floor and wall use. They are resistant to water absorption, which makes them ideal for high-moisture areas such as bathrooms and kitchens. Due to their non-porous nature, they are easy to clean and maintain, making them a popular choice for modern interiors. Suitable for both walls and floors, and can be used in living rooms, bedrooms, bathrooms, kitchens, and even commercial spaces. This type of tile is a good choice for modern interior designs that require both functionality and style.','White','Ceramic, Glossy, Industrial, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3db61c7-18a2-3141-67a6-a5be68d2e22/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3e7708-35c5-4bd1-58f-a248ddd31318/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/563b1e4-1750-6bf6-2bb4-ecfa4773afa4/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/563b1e4-1750-6bf6-2bb4-ecfa4773afa4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/567f2b6-bcb2-c5e-7e3f-7e473ac421/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5b768d8-1467-5611-be56-fff5ecb36211/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7dbef7-0880-bf56-6e04-a2162fda45b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products