(210,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Onyx Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Blue Floor and Wall Tile Code32608 (600x1200mm, Matt)',91,'Elevate your interiors with our premium 600x1200mm vitrified tile, designed for both floor and wall applications. Known for its durability, low water absorption, and seamless finish, this large-format tile adds a touch of elegance and spaciousness to any residential or commercial space. Perfect for creating modern, sleek surfaces that are easy to maintain and long-lasting. Transform your space with our 600x1200mm vitrified tiles, crafted for modern living. These large-format tiles offer a sleek, seamless look with minimal grout lines, enhancing the visual appeal of floors and walls alike. Highly durable, stain-resistant, and easy to clean, they are ideal for both residential and commercial interiors where style meets functionality. Add depth and character to your interiors with our 600x1200mm textured vitrified tiles. Designed to mimic natural surfaces with refined textures, these tiles bring a tactile charm while offering the superior strength and stain resistance of vitrified material. Perfect for statement walls, feature floors, or medium-traffic areas.','Blue, Red','Modern, Natural, Textured, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0ac4e0-742-17a0-671-24dc8cdbc64b/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0ac4e0-742-17a0-671-24dc8cdbc64b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2ec03cb-6a0d-8614-da3f-f0c5b032c7ec/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/688ccfa-77eb-4681-d8e0-e4562c1612f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6bf4fe7-08c0-7b44-456c-622833ff8ec/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6f78b6d-71ea-6c1d-18ef-a6f5010786db/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/st