(243,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / 15Mm Thick Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified White 15mm Slab Floor and Wall Tile Code37100 (1200x1800mm, Glossy)',135,'The Vitrified 15mm Slab Floor and Wall Tile is designed to deliver superior strength, refined aesthetics, and long-lasting performance for both residential and commercial spaces. Manufactured using high-density vitrified technology with a solid 15mm thickness, this slab tile offers exceptional durability, load-bearing capacity, and resistance to impact, making it ideal for high-traffic areas. Its large slab format creates a seamless, expansive look with minimal grout lines, enhancing the overall visual appeal of floors and walls. The smooth, premium surface finish adds a touch of sophistication while being resistant to stains, scratches, moisture, and daily wear. Easy to clean and maintain, this tile ensures a hygienic and long-lasting surface. Suitable for living rooms, bedrooms, kitchens, bathrooms, feature walls, lobbies, and commercial interiors, the Vitrified 15mm Slab Tile brings together modern elegance, structural strength, and versatile design for contemporary architectural spaces.','Red, White','Contemporary, Glossy, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/006212-842-f52d-4762-dcad425cf276/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/04cb11-0a5-7fb-1a12-084324b2ac16/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/33d5f3f-070-a1ad-770-5c358daf6531/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4b5c8a-50ee-06d3-f0f4-26fc8ae5506f/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4b5c8a-50ee-06d3-f0f4-26fc8ae5506f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5eafcbd-d607-d722-b601-7ef7e0e84b3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5fc8ad-643