(261,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Anti Skid Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Black Digital Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code29928 (300x300mm,Matt)',51,'Parking and high-movement zones require flooring that combines grip, impact resistance, and visual clarity. This black digital parking tile, Code 29928, comes in a 300x300 mm matte finish that keeps surface glare low while reinforcing digital pattern detail. Vitrified manufacturing creates a dense body with low absorption and improved resistance to surface wear, making it appropriate for areas needing both strength and performance continuity. The black tone acts as a base that hides light marks and dust, while the digital texture helps mask surface variation under heavy movement. Its compact format supports stable installation with controlled joint alignment, which helps distribute weight and minimise stress points. Matt surface reduces shine that can cause glare under bright artificial or natural light, supporting safer movement. Vitrified bodies resist water absorption and staining better than many standard tiles, and routine care remains simple with sweeping and damp mopping. This tile is engineered to handle frequent use, balancing practical performance with a composed, uniform appearance that blends with structured environments.','Black, Light, Red','Digital, Matte, Natural, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3e615db-0770-40a-77e7-42b21a1e65/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4c6f288-02d-cf6-027d-3ff48dc802b6/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4c6f288-02d-cf6-027d-3ff48dc802b6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5d3a1e6-a6cd-8ce0-da6b-575ff11602/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/884266d-41b4-5183-7c24-66e238a3f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/p