(273,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Anti Skid Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Gray Digital Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code31040 (300x300mm, Matt)',55,'A 300x300mm Vitrified Parking Tile is a durable and high-performance tile commonly used for parking areas, driveways, and other high-traffic zones. Vitrified tiles are manufactured through a process of vitrification, where they are heated at high temperatures to ensure a dense, non-porous surface, making them resistant to water absorption, stains, and wear. Vitrified tiles are known for their high strength and resistance to abrasion, making them perfect for heavy vehicles and frequent foot traffic. Most vitrified parking tiles come with anti-slip features, reducing the risk of accidents in wet conditions. Available in various colors and designs, these tiles can enhance the visual appeal of outdoor spaces while maintaining functionality. These tiles are resistant to various weather conditions, including heat, cold, and moisture, ensuring long-lasting performance.','Gray, Red','Digital, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/286c205-85d8-8235-10e4-d103824e463/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/64d0f4d-ea25-0ada-3a8e-31fb53d2c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/742861-56c-6ee-2c4a-aa5eb5dcf41/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c105c55-f7a2-822-b4f-bba0d25f26/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c181c13-4355-2ba0-5e2a-47558a547d/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c181c13-4355-2ba0-5e2a-47558a547d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d1fac-0346-0c3f-8b55-b76ff33ebd2/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e3426e-353e-6c2-ccf-e2ed0371ab1/600x600.webp','300x30