(282,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Anti Skid Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Parking Tile Code17274 (390x390mm, Matt)',77,'Evoking the feeling of stone finishes and the earthiness of natural stones, this collection of vitrified parking tiles by MyTyles is a result of natural surfaces reimagined. With a striking propensity to craft sophisticated surfaces in a jiffy, these digitally printed parking tiles facilitate breathtaking end-to-end transformations with the speckles, tonal undulations that deliver a textural difference, and a gentle movement characteristic of palatial remodels anywhere. With the unique capability to craft seamless, continuous surfaces in lieu of the rectified edges and a soft matte glaze replicating a honed polish look, these large-format vitrified tiles are available in three sombre shades. The sleek design paired with the utilitarian benefits makes this 16 x 16 inch vitrified parking tile a true force of human intervention. Elevating the mood of every room just got simpler.','Red','Digital, Matte, Natural, Printed, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0def4e8-2774-11fb-528b-fc355da178dd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/38c048-250a-023-2ad1-287ac2a27c4a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8311a5-42ca-fd6-72b3-86505c3bbb0a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b2cef6-a65a-54a5-474f-7f0ba13a13b4/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b2cef6-a65a-54a5-474f-7f0ba13a13b4/600x600.webp','390x390mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-parking-tile-code17274-390x390mm-matt'),
(283,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Anti Skid Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Gray Digital Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code31039 (300x300mm, Matt)',55,'A 300x300mm Vitrified Parking Tile is a durable and high-performance tile commonly used for parking areas, driveways, and other high-traffic zones. Vitrified tiles are manufactured through a process of vitrification, where they are heated at high temperatures to ensure a dense, non-porous surface, making them resistant to water absorption, stains, and wear. Vitrified tiles are known for their high strength and resistance to abrasion, making them perfect for heavy vehicles and frequent foot traffic. Most vitrified parking tiles come with anti-slip features, reducing the risk of accidents in wet conditions. Available in various colors and designs, these tiles can enhance the visual appeal of outdoor spaces while maintaining functionality. These tiles are resistant to various weather conditions, including heat, cold, and moisture, ensuring long-lasting performance.','Gray, Red','Digital, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0bcc157-f5b-23e-8c55-d1c23bc62702/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2282c-f40c-5565-e707-43cd43f1a8c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/847fc2b-45c2-a77d-82e0-5410a023a6b/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/847fc2b-45c2-a77d-82e0-5410a023a6b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/85378e-735-3050-d581-4a16d22efd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a1ffe4-612a-5bf4-6dee-a63defc80aa/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/eb376e7-304f-2e26-d8c-2b263f5368c5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/edcd323-c432-6611-a01-2e8db71ac56a/600x600.webp'