(288,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Glossy Vitrified Tiles','White and Gold Highlighter Wall Tile Code17976 (300x600mm, Glossy)',864,'Alternating between crisp, solid intersecting lines and striated beehive patterns, this glossy vitrified wall tile by MyTyles sets the tone for any space without impeaching on the decor style or the aesthetics. Set on a snow white base glaze, the sparse grey ribbons run throughout of the body of the 2 x 1 feet vitrified tile. The luminous interplay of stress and wider ribbons collectively give the impression of an authentic Italian Calcatta marble whereas the stylistic positioning of beehive patterns create a geometric effect. Designed to resist the strongest of external agents, the reflective glossy glaze further amplifies the graceful presence of this vitrified tile in your indoor wall facade. A reflection of true, productive human intervention this large format vitrified wall tile exemplifies the best fine craftsmanship that is both attainable and usable.','Gold, Grey, Light, White','Geometric, Glossy, Large Format, Marble, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/06424f3-5e72-5edc-3054-3e2b23f8b2ed/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/172386-67d1-7f4b-b26-71348ba6ff/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/182ecd-4835-7ac-b3e7-e4ffde28080/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/31b5430-1ebd-ce-0885-25445878f81a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3c5646-dc12-4e4-7e-e7ebc8dba778/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3c5646-dc12-4e4-7e-e7ebc8dba778/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/50f87f1-b418-351-8f4-b0afe672f7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/87f71f8-5c8f-c54-33b7-0fa6