(289,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Glossy Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Black Madam Mosaic Poster Wall Tile Code34198 (4x8 Feet, Glossy)',10500,'Madam Poster Wall Tile features a striking and elegant design, perfect for adding a sophisticated touch to any interior wall. Crafted from premium ceramic/porcelain with a glossy finish, this tile showcases detailed artwork that blends modern aesthetics with timeless charm. Ideal for living rooms, bedrooms, offices, or feature walls, the tile offers durability, easy maintenance, and vibrant colors that remain vivid over time. Madam Poster Wall Tile is a premium decorative tile that combines artistic elegance with durable craftsmanship. Featuring a beautifully detailed portrait-style design of a sophisticated madam figure, this tile adds a touch of grace and refinement to any interior space. The vibrant, high-resolution print is protected by a glossy, smooth finish that enhances the colors and makes cleaning effortless. Ideal for accent walls, lounges, boutiques, cafes, or stylish living areas, this tile transforms ordinary walls into captivating art displays. Its robust ceramic or porcelain construction ensures longevity and resistance to moisture, making it suitable for both residential and commercial applications.','Black, Vibrant','Artistic, Ceramic, Decorative, Glossy, Modern, Mosaic, Porcelain, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/076fd46-ab1-64b1-580-443d587c8b26/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/076fd46-ab1-64b1-580-443d587c8b26/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1d36683-8153-207b-1428-58cbc60eb1f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1fb50eb-bafb-c33-a71f-8307ed51d1d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6da77ac-074e-2f7-b736-5023a8ff88cb/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/s