(290,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Glossy Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Lord Shiva Poster Wall Tile Code32592 (600x900mm, Glossy)-CR-3036',7500,'Invoke divine energy and artistic elegance into your space with the 600x900mm Vitrified Lord Shiva Poster Wall Tile. Crafted with precision and reverence, this stunning decorative tile captures the powerful and serene presence of Lord Shiva, making it an ideal centerpiece for spiritual and aesthetic environments. Channel the energy of the cosmos into your living or spiritual space with our 600x900mm Vitrified Lord Shiva Poster Wall Tile. Designed to be more than just décor, this divine tile embodies the power, tranquility, and symbolism of Mahadev the Supreme Lord. Perfectly suited for modern homes as well as traditional interiors, this tile fuses artistic devotion with technical excellence, creating a piece that is both sacred and stunning.','Red','Artistic, Decorative, Glossy, Modern, Traditional, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/17a42c0-680b-bfe-fb0f-00e1a01470d4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/274d3a3-34ec-c37f-330-063e27f1c1e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/612235f-40d4-aff2-0cae-2bc2556c8fb/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/612235f-40d4-aff2-0cae-2bc2556c8fb/600x600.webp','600x900mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-lord-shiva-poster-wall-tile-code32592-600x900mm-glossy-cr-3036'),
(291,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Glossy Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Radha Krishna Poster Wall Tile Code30992 (4x6ft, Glossy,3Pcs)',11800,'Immerse yourself in the enchanting spiritual aura with this stunning Lord Radha Krishna poster. Featuring the eternal divine couple in a moment of grace, this artwork beautifully captures the love and devotion between Radha and Krishna. The glossy finish enhances the vibrant colors, creating a radiant glow that brings the scene to life. The intricate details and the serene expressions evoke a sense of peace and divine connection, making it a perfect addition to any sacred space, living room, or meditation area. Let the divine energy of Radha Krishna fill your surroundings with love, joy, and harmony.','Red, Vibrant','Glossy, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2b54847-a3a-0262-45db-b43710e4e6ad/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2b54847-a3a-0262-45db-b43710e4e6ad/600x600.webp','4x6ft','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-radha-krishna-poster-wal-til-code30992-4x6ft-glossy'),
(292,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Glossy Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Orange Buddha Poster Wall Tile Code34973(2x3 Feet, Glossy)-CR-3094',7500,'Introduce a steady flow of contemporary warmth in your residential and commercial properties with this 2 x 3 feet Buddha vitrfied mural wall tile by MyTyles. Dripping with vintage charm, this vitrified tile is decorated with Buddha seated on a lotus engraved seat with a saffron garment against the ashoka chakra on the background. Decorated with numerous numerous realistic detailing and dainty detailing including cadmium, ceylon lime, and bronze with pops of blue and sienna respectively. Crafted with the glistening satin matte glaze, this vitrified mural tile is rich, visually appealing and creates brilliant focal points for your accent wall installations whether used in indoor or semi-outdoor settings including living areas, hallways, corridors and more. Repellant to dust, grime, chips, cracks, discolouration, and other forms of wear and tear, this mural wall tile crafts low maintenance and nevertheless elegant installations wherever it goes.','Blue, Orange','Contemporary, Glossy, Matte, Satin, Vintage, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2f5c1c4-a55-cde-a18-3aea354173c8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5a1f67f-20ac-0805-183-6de224efc8d5/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5a1f67f-20ac-0805-183-6de224efc8d5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/671a72d-25d-0420-3420-c0e8671fd23/600x600.webp','2x3','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-orange-buddha-poster-wall-tile-code34973-2x3-feet-glossy-cr-3094'),
