(296,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Glossy Vitrified Tiles','Krishna With Leaf Poster Wall Tile Code32595 (600x900mm, Glossy)-CR-3007',7500,'Embrace peace, innocence, and divine charm with the Krishna with Leaf Poster Wall Tile a serene portrayal of Lord Krishna as a child, resting gently on a vibrant leaf. Symbolic of purity, protection, and the divine play of the universe, this artwork blends mythology with modern décor, creating a sacred focal point for any space. Printed in high-definition on vitrified ceramic, the tile features intricate detailing, vivid colors, and a radiant finish that lasts for years making it perfect for pooja rooms, meditation spaces, or even as a spiritual gift. The image of Krishna resting on a leaf is inspired by sacred texts a vision of innocence amidst eternity, a child who holds the cosmos in his breath. Whether you seek to create a calm devotional space or add a touch of sacred art to your home, this tile is more than decoration it is a blessing in form.','Red, Vibrant','Ceramic, Glossy, Modern, Printed, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/62fee00-3b3-4b1c-4c7-0008422cabe/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6e84aca-611c-b387-c647-0e617c85a653/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6e84aca-611c-b387-c647-0e617c85a653/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a04387f-62b0-5fa2-0d58-e400ec180fa/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/fc0fe8-5730-24a5-1cc5-cb828ac07b03/600x600.webp','600x900mm','https://mytyles.com/product/krishna-with-leaf-poster-wall-tile-code32595-600x900mm-glossy-cr-3007'),
