(299,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Glossy Vitrified Tiles','Imported Blue Subway Wall Tile Code38048 (50x500mm, Glossy)',1200,'The 50x500mm Imported Ceramic Glossy Finish Subway Wall Tile is a stylish and contemporary choice for enhancing interior walls. Featuring a sleek elongated subway format and a glossy surface, this tile reflects light beautifully, creating a bright and spacious feel in any room. The glossy finish adds a smooth, polished look that brings elegance and a modern touch to walls while making the surface easy to clean and maintain. Crafted from high-quality imported ceramic, these tiles offer durability, moisture resistance, and long-lasting performance, making them ideal for areas such as kitchen backsplashes, bathroom walls, shower areas, and decorative feature walls. The slim 50x500mm size allows for creative installation patterns like vertical stacking, horizontal layouts, or herringbone designs, adding versatility to interior design.','Blue, Light','Ceramic, Contemporary, Decorative, Glossy, Herringbone, Modern, Polished, Subway','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/040185d-efad-b6b6-5c03-c2106e2cfed5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/26455f-f6e5-52d7-558-886a82aa5e76/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/62de740-0513-853f-befd-d475860662de/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/68d282f-2cc0-0d3d-3ce3-d61036c3a6e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6abe7f3-88c0-b06f-64bb-f5f07b563a4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d285005-77c6-3026-a68e-b67b53aa28/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/fbdb43a-2507-a56-2e8-41261d130304/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/fbdb43a-2507-a56-2e8-41261d130304/600x600.webp','50x500mm','https://mytyles.com/product/imported-blue-subway-wall-tile-code38048-50x500mm-glossy'),
(300,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Glossy Vitrified Tiles','Double Charge Vitrified Floor and Wall Tile Code31918 (800x800mm, Glossy)',76,'This 2x2 Feet Vitrified Glossy Finish Floor and Wall Tile offers a sophisticated and versatile option for both floor and wall applications. Made from high-quality vitrified ceramic material, it provides exceptional durability and resistance to stains, moisture, and wear, making it ideal for high-traffic areas like kitchens, bathrooms, living rooms, or even commercial spaces. The glossy finish ensures a subtle, reflective surface that complements a wide range of interior styles, offering a modern yet timeless appeal. Its smooth, even texture provides comfort underfoot while maintaining an elegant and understated look on walls. This tile is easy to maintain, providing long-lasting beauty with minimal upkeep. Perfect for creating a cohesive and refined aesthetic in any space.','','Ceramic, Double Charge, Glossy, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6355fe4-0572-71b2-3a7-73babda4beff/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/67de46-415f-0e-e110-a4e75e2ce1af/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/77d0d0e-e70f-d61-587c-bb43122055/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/84e730-ce62-414-be4f-7a83802dbe12/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/87152-284-4141-2c13-c0517641546/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a4848ac-2fe8-0cc-636f-0c37fdcbd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c0c3165-2c4-44b-bdd8-b6ca845610fa/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d2054d4-332-d2be-3534-6ab01bc0c14/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d2054d4-332-