(301,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Glossy Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Golden Buddha Poster Wall Tile Code32589 (4x6 Feet, Glossy)',21800,'Create a serene and luxurious ambiance with Golden Buddha Design Poster Wall Glossy Tiles. Crafted with a high-gloss finish and intricate golden detailing, these tiles reflect peace, spirituality, and elegance. Perfect for meditation rooms, living spaces, or statement walls, the Golden Buddha design adds a divine and tranquil touch to modern interiors. Durable, easy to clean, and visually captivating, these glossy tiles elevate your décor with timeless beauty and harmony.','Gold','Glossy, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0324f7-4-8ba8-4151-ae2d773ce414/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2045af5-7a7d-ad23-a2dc-1dbdcef05524/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2045af5-7a7d-ad23-a2dc-1dbdcef05524/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e64a35a-b335-386c-8176-6408c08e8342/600x600.webp','4x6','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-golden-buddha-poster-wall-tile-code32589-4x6-feet-glossy'),
(302,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Glossy Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Ganesha Poster Wall Tile Code23510 (600x900mm, Glossy)',3750,'A fine blend of metallic accents and heavy textures, this 2 x 3 feet Ganesha vitrified mural wall tile by MyTyles adds a mid-century European aesthetic to your decor. Featuring big, bold metallic lines and the stoic presence of Lord Ganesha, the body of this vitrified wall tile is finished with faux speckles and freckles to give your decor an artisanal, handcrafted quality. Incorporating copper and bronze toned finishes on a slate grey backdrop, this vitrified wall tile adds an authentic vintage touch to your accent walls. Apt for a myriad of decor styles, this double fired vitrified mural tile is suited for a wide range of indoor and semi-outdoor remodels in residential and commercial settings. Sturdy, durable, and incredibly low maintenance, this vitrified wall tile make a practical choice at the fraction of the cost, maintenance and installation efforts.','Grey, Metallic, Red','Glossy, Slate, Vintage, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/522ee2-6d42-e1db-abb-68ad73b472/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7808cc-c178-83a-664a-f8bcc7d443/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b111cf0-c01a-05e-ccec-747ef8ee275/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b5260d1-4cf-dd17-4141-45bffdc5c08/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/bf21e12-00a5-ad4-ef61-db3b7d7a5dd7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e2bcb03-bb0-80e-483b-67f8f4fbf76f/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e2bcb03-bb0-80e-483b-67f8f4fbf76f/600x600.webp','600x900mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-ganesha-poster-wall-tile-code23510-600x900mm-glossy'),
(303,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Glossy Vitrified Tiles','Krishna Playing Flute Poster Wall Tile Code33208 (4x6 Feet, Glossy)-CR-1003',21800,'Bring home the serenity of divine music with the Krishna Playing Flute Wall Tile a stunning representation of Lord Krishna in his most iconic and beloved form. With his enchanting flute, peacock feather crown, and divine smile, Krishna symbolizes peace, love, and cosmic harmony. This tile is not just wall art its a spiritual experience that transforms any space with its calming presence. Crafted using high-definition digital printing on vitrified ceramic, this tile captures the intricate beauty of Krishnas divine form from the delicate fingers holding the flute to the serene expression that invites devotion. It''s perfect for those who wish to blend traditional spirituality with modern décor aesthetics. The Krishna Playing Flute Wall Tile is more than just décor its a symbol of harmony, a spiritual accent, and a timeless reminder of divine love. Add it to your space and let Lord Krishnas presence elevate your surroundings with calm and positivity.','','Ceramic, Digital, Glossy, Modern, Traditional, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/11d25e-ec20-08a2-6b16-6eb56fba5511/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/11d25e-ec20-08a2-6b16-6eb56fba5511/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/320d0ce-baa3-c542-876b-f0bb24e27c0/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/527ed62-5f14-e8d-ceea-73fdb23541ad/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a28f225-a167-583b-a704-28841a1ba7cf/600x600.webp','4x6','https://mytyles.com/product/krishna-playing-flute-poster-wall-tile-code33208-4x6-feet-glossy-cr-1003'),
