(316,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Matt Vitrified Tiles','Multi Color Mughal Mural Wall Tile Code31924 (4x6Feet, Glossy/Matt,3Pcs)',25200,'A Mughal Set Tile is a type of decorative tile inspired by the iconic art and architectural style of the Mughal Empire, which flourished in South Asia from the 16th to the 18th centuries. These tiles feature intricate patterns, rich colors, and detailed motifs that reflect the grandeur and elegance of Mughal design. Often seen in palaces, mosques, and royal buildings, Mughal tiles add a regal and timeless beauty to any space. The design of these tiles is heavily influenced by Mughal architecture, which combines Persian, Indian, and Central Asian art forms. The motifs commonly include floral patterns, geometric shapes, arches, and intricate calligraphy, all contributing to a rich, ornate aesthetic. Mughal Set Tiles bring a sense of royal elegance and artistic sophistication to any space, blending rich historical influences with modern design sensibilities. They are perfect for anyone looking to infuse their space with luxury, history, and intricate beauty.','Red','Artistic, Decorative, Floral, Geometric, Glossy, Modern','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0cc1ed1-ae2-fd82-75b5-32d5b3c8b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/412cd8e-bb22-231b-a572-5dbfb4254dee/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/412cd8e-bb22-231b-a572-5dbfb4254dee/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4c32346-722-166-d5ed-318f4d115f1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7f772a-1272-125d-a57-04c087e23b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d02fffa-5f2e-ccb5-4748-3842ddc0653/600x600.webp','4x6Feet','https://mytyles.com/product/multi-color-mughal-mural-wall-tile-code31924-4x6ft-glossy-matt'),
