(339,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Black Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code3329 (300x300mm, Matt)',210,'Bring home the vibrancy with this mosaic grid 12 x 12 inch Moroccan wall and floor tile by MyTyles. Featuring a mix of creamy white and charcoal black against a beaded, the body of this vitrified wall and floor tile is divided into numerous small squares in a beautiful smoke grey outline. Followed by slight dips in texture, alternate concentric squares lends a unique modern touch while uplifting any space with its simplistic charm. The ridged lines acts as an illusion of painstakingly assembled smaller tiles minus the inconvenience of battling impossible choices to execute the strenous job to the dot. Flaunt this matte finished Moroccan tile as a kitchen or sink backsplash, a vintage living room, kitchen, bathroom, or bedroom floor wall facade, or revamp utilitarian areas like mudrooms, powder rooms, laundry areas, foyer areas, front porches and more. For an indoor vertical installation or accent piece, deepen the faux grooves with a dremel and fill them with grout in a natural or industrial tint of your choice or match with other printed tiles of your choice to invite an element of a flush, decadent finesse to your residential or commercial properties.','Black, Charcoal, Cream, Grey, Light, Mix, White','Industrial, Matte, Modern, Mosaic, Natural, Printed, Square, Vintage, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/135dc21-7a8e-3d7e-2e0f-b38b10d301e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/324a0f6-2f58-ea5-eb81-b77b877604/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/42df6b-ca8-85c-b8dc-c45c2e3410f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/83a6e-c3ee-4450-6a5e-3a428ed4cf6d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d4d48-7ff5-ea1c-ea6-acd0ba742e7f/1200x120