(341,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Black Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Elevation Tile Code8081 (300x600mm, Matt)',75,'An amalgamation of marble finish and stone textures, the Storm Collection from MyTyles redefines elevation wall tiles as we know them. Complete with a matte glaze, the 3D detailing on this vitrified tile is met with a captivating and enamouring gaze wherever it goes. The amalgamation of marble-like veining on both the textured frames and sparse across the smooth shapes add an ultramodern finish to an otherwise traditional mosaic arrangement. Rectified edges further reduce the grout lines to almost non-existent to make your installation mimic the look of stone cladding at the fraction of the price. Available in two colours, the Brown variation uses warm tones of beige, sand, and mocha for bringing out the 3D textures. Nero sports an off-white body with shades of maritime blue and Prussian Blue to add ultimate sophistication to the 2 x 1 feet large format design. Perfect for both residential and commercial remodelling projects, these vitrified elevation tiles can be used in wall decoration outdoors, indoors and in common transitional spaces like entryways, hallways, or verandas. Convenient, reliable, and graceful, this elevation wall tile becomes a lasting companion to both residential and commercial settings.','Beige, Blue, Brown, Red, White','Large Format, Marble, Matte, Modern, Mosaic, Textured, Traditional, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0f3b844-703-5620-1cc8-0336fa0a1c81/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1dd2087-ea1-770c-f22a-7fc74db885e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2bbc32b-a6ff-3565-870-3de2ffdeb057/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/33cf44-767-b6f7-d4ed-847b12c50f/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/