(344,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Black Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Tile Code20349 (600x600mm, Carving Matt)',71,'An impressive amalgamation of rustic minimalism and stupendous digital printing technology, this 2 x 2 feet vitrified wall and floor tile by MyTyles renders a sophisticated touch to your home. Slight tonal undulations couples with the subtle sheen from the matte glaze to add the right blend of elegance and minimalism. A snug fit for all sorts of residential and commercial remodels, this double fired vitrified tile is as humble as it is accommodating. The smokey grey liases well with a variety of decor styles and color schemes. Refashion semi-outdoor and intdoor areas with this carved, anti-slip vitrified tile. Reliable and resilient by nature, this large format vitrified tile is laden with functionality and versatility that ascertains longevity and the beauty of your surfaces without the added stress and efforts to leave the surfaces looking brand new.','Grey, Light, Red','Carving, Digital, Large Format, Matte, Rustic, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/637a6dc-3e48-43db-b13-ea584371785b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8a871b1-40a1-c05-d2da-b1874c54033/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8c3635a-0560-64c-10c-60120d3a045a/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8c3635a-0560-64c-10c-60120d3a045a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ac7872-057-8a5b-281f-c2a25f3c3b1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b2d8572-6d2c-5182-00a5-1c4d4186e3b0/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/f26428e-fbfe-e4d6-7fd-6b1dce007345/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/f4d5f72-3251-461d-680-64d3ae68a6e/600x600.