(350,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Black Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Black Border Tile Code33810 (100x1200mm, Glossy)',800,'Vitrified Border Tile is a stylish finishing element designed to enhance the look of walls and floors. Made from premium vitrified material, these tiles are highly durable, scratch-resistant, and stain-proof, making them suitable for both residential and commercial spaces. With their sleek design and elegant patterns, border tiles add definition, create visual separation, and bring a decorative accent to any tile layout. Ideal for use in living rooms, kitchens, bathrooms, and corridors, they not only elevate aesthetics but also ensure long-lasting performance with minimal maintenance. Vitrified Border Tile is a premium decorative tile crafted to add a refined touch to your walls and floors. Manufactured using advanced vitrification technology, these tiles are denser, more durable, and less porous than regular ceramic tiles, ensuring long-lasting beauty with minimal upkeep. The elegant border design makes it perfect for framing wall layouts, defining spaces, or adding a striking contrast to plain tiles. Whether you want to highlight a backsplash, outline a hallway, or enhance the edges of a feature wall, vitrified border tiles bring structure and sophistication to any interior or exterior setting.','Black, Light, Red','Ceramic, Decorative, Glossy, Plain, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2cf0ebc-357b-20f0-4ce5-33f075585d0d/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2cf0ebc-357b-20f0-4ce5-33f075585d0d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/557ed6f-b57b-be64-28bb-fb4f15f5044f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/56f464a-7845-f300-5408-e8a07340087/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7b31f2e-8b44-5301-2cb1-c47f6a3ba4e/600x600