(370,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Grey Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Multi Color Textured Wall Tile Code37020 (600x1200mm, Matt)',125,'Elevate your interiors with the refined sophistication of the 600x1200mm vitrified textured wall tile, designed for modern spaces that demand both style and strength. Crafted using advanced vitrification technology, this tile offers exceptional density, low porosity, and lasting durability, making it ideal for both residential and commercial applications. Its textured surface adds depth and dimension, creating a visually engaging wall finish that effortlessly enhances any décor themefrom contemporary minimalism to elegant luxury. The subtle variations in tone and texture replicate the natural beauty of stone, giving your walls a premium, organic aesthetic without compromising on performance. Its generous 600x1200mm format provides a seamless, expansive look with fewer joints, resulting in a cleaner, more sophisticated finish. Stain-resistant, moisture-proof, and easy to maintain, this vitrified wall tile is as practical as it is beautiful, making it perfect for living rooms, feature walls, lobbies, bathrooms, and high-impact design spaces.','Red','Contemporary, Modern, Natural, Textured, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0784e4-5b8e-d283-ed01-440bdc4ac67f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1b632aa-f778-6653-e511-46da50c1f8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4067ee-ce3a-7287-847b-73eeb7c5c3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4a3f7af-74d3-d4f-2043-bc186cebaf0c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6edc15b-5b08-24b4-834-2713d1aa/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/74b4f0a-60e-2b80-a81f-f237c224537/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod