27-600x900mm-glossy'),
(383,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Grey Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Floor and Wall Tile Code2629 (300x1200mm, Matt)',111,'This collection of 1 x 4 feet vitrified wall and floor tiles by MyTyles amplifies the inherent beauty of your space. Riddled with faux speckles and scuffs, the top notch digital prints on these vitrified plank tiles add undeniable depth and dimension to your wall and floor installations. Available in two variations, solid and embossed, both the variants sport similar prints and textures. However, the embossed variant is decorated with ridged, notched exteriors. Complete with the fine lustre, the textures and tones in both the variants are a curious mix of intriguing and delicate impressionism. Whether used to craft exquisite floors in the kitchen, bedroom or living room, or an accent tapestry on the walls in the entryway or balcony, this collection of vitrified wall and floor slabs always shines through. Sturdy, durable, and ageless, these vitrified slabs fit in any residential and commercial setting.','Mix','Digital, Plank, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/01d0fc-c5eb-e501-7ba-42c6e4cdd71d/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/01d0fc-c5eb-e501-7ba-42c6e4cdd71d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0acbdb8-1574-adc0-f0f8-f27162e2db/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7172802-4d5d-8b46-bacf-a3265b134e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8bfc1-eedf-77a5-e4cb-7c8f532eb5e1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/cc6e6c2-cb0a-de0-ae-6de707ff870/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d625da5-83d5-7148-431-3e011be0b3c3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d6d4e6-bfb4-2a07-63b8-bda42413767