(386,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Grey Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code23054 (600x600mm, Matt)',296,'Capturing the essence of dynamic visual appeal and alternating patterns, this collection of 2 x 2 feet Moroccan wall and floor tiles by MyTyles thrives when relaying its contemporary warmth. With a penchant to create captivating visual effects through muted tones and clean lines, the geometric patterns on these double fired vitrified tiles are fairly versatile. Redefining spaces through its characteristic Moroccan graphic aesthetic, the matte glaze and the soothing palette can blend into any space irrespective of the decor style. Available in two color palettes, cerulean with ruby accents and gray with seafoam detailing, this collection imbues a sense of cohesiveness in your spaces. With interlocking edges, these vitrified wall and floor tiles impart a trendsetting display of geometric patterns that can be laid out in a stacked arrangement for a one piece effect whether used as a kitchen backsplash, floors, shower surrounds, bathrooms, mudrooms, balcony or entryways. Elevate the space without clashing with your aesthetics, these large format Moroccan tiles are a humble blend of quality craftsmanship and stunning good looks.','Gray, Red','Contemporary, Geometric, Large Format, Matte, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/123763-3e40-c5c-dbd-874d1bb8fa7c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/61b61eb-2ff7-ec13-cc1-d7bd52b454a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6455c30-c541-02d1-d5fb-b413a0b7a7eb/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6bd70-edea-bbb5-27c6-28eb202672e7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b407db-e8ce-7245-fcb-875c380b2dd2/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/bade876-0c-3