(387,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Grey Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code3325 (300x300mm, Matt)',210,'Marrying 3D geometric shapes with charming colours, this vitrified wall and floor tile from MyTyles creates an elusive wall or floor installation. Capitalizing on the generous use of repetitive diamond shapes and triangles, the design is crafted to welcome unusual depth and dimension into your interiors. The central motif looks like a 3D star, creating an optical illusion. Harmonizing the space with its metropolitan aesthetic, the 12 x 12 inches large format body, makes this Moroccan tile easy to install. Suitable for a multitude of remodel projects, use this vitrified tile to redesign kitchen backsplashes and floors, bathroom backsplashes and floors, shower surrounds, or an end-to-end bathroom renovation. Slip-resistant and extraordinarily sturdy, they make fabulous semi-outdoor floors, e.g., garage floors, mudrooms, living rooms, bedrooms, balconies, and terraces. Available in two colours, ash grey, and yellow ochre, they harmonize the aesthetics and utilitarian aspects to bring a wholesome feel to any surface.','Grey, Red, Yellow','Geometric, Large Format, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/143b212-57d0-16bf-c6e0-020dcfec5b8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2ab206-5b6f-25de-20a6-b28f8ece018/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/34dc73-1b04-ed4-f481-b4acf3581a3b/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/34dc73-1b04-ed4-f481-b4acf3581a3b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a53d836-5a71-fd2e-3b7-a747a4fb4bc7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/cdfe621-6d2d-0478-a647-6b8e552654/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/eab4fae-47dc-482-8