(390,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Grey Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Grey Digital Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code28775 (300x300mm, Matt)',42,'Enhance the functionality and appearance of your parking area with 1x1 feet digital parking matte finish tiles. These tiles are engineered for strength and durability, making them perfect for high-traffic areas like driveways, garages, and outdoor spaces. The matte finish not only adds a contemporary look but also offers slip resistance, ensuring safety even in wet conditions. With digital printing technology, these tiles feature realistic designs that maintain their vibrancy and texture over time. Easy to clean and maintain, theyre a practical and stylish choice for any outdoor surface requiring long-lasting performance.','Grey, Red','Contemporary, Digital, Matte, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/074a1-e755-8f2a-422c-d86a4064fc8d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/085226-5705-7114-f4b-c06c75de0c1d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1fa574e-e617-83e1-3581-547fc4556e71/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2fcb35d-ce40-f6b-3aca-21c2f5fe208/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2fcb35d-ce40-f6b-3aca-21c2f5fe208/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/607e38-e4e0-045b-b01c-d4e13efcd4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6feea56-1f1a-37ea-d188-16535eda61ed/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d384357-31b-8858-4e70-7b1526dfe/600x600.webp','300x300mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-grey-digital-parking-floor-and-wall-tile-code28775-300x300mm-matt'),
(391,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Grey Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Gray Floor and Wall Tile Code24057 (600x1200mm, Matt)',84,'Enhance the beauty and functionality of your interiors with our 2x4 feet vitrified matt floor and wall tiles. Designed to elevate the look of any space, these high-quality ceramic tiles offer a sleek, shiny finish that complements modern aesthetics. The vitrified surface ensures superior durability, stain resistance, and easy maintenance, making them perfect for high-traffic areas such as kitchens, bathrooms, living rooms, and commercial spaces. With their large format size, these tiles create a seamless, contemporary look, reducing grout lines for a smoother finish. Whether for flooring or wall applications, these tiles provide a stylish and long-lasting solution to suit any design preference.','Gray, Red','Ceramic, Contemporary, Large Format, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2cc5c46-c6b-e0-f4ad-c6b251056/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/462625-48f0-b8f-5d4b-0e4677e4a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4b4b400-8b6c-a4c2-aa6b-561a837103a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4fddd08-3cc-631c-d766-5085840ddd17/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4fddd08-3cc-631c-d766-5085840ddd17/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5df0d5-435f-f1b2-d67-4e3cfb75dc5a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6aca2e6-5f1-618c-50ac-82d75684bdf/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8487e4-5710-12bf-51fe-7561baca87d5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b6b632-e817-4f5a-f807-3424c088e5e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storag