(398,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Beige Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Beige Modular Floor and Wall Tile Code35125 (500x500mm, Matt)',101,'The Modular Design Tile brings a perfect balance of style and flexibility to your interiors. Crafted with precision, these tiles feature interlocking patterns that can be arranged in various layouts, allowing endless design possibilities. Ideal for creating unique flooring or accent walls, they blend modern aesthetics with practical durability. Suitable for living rooms, kitchens, bathrooms, and commercial spaces, modular tiles offer easy installation and a timeless, coordinated look. The Modular Design Tile is a versatile and stylish choice for both residential and commercial interiors. Its unique modular pattern allows you to create endless combinations, from symmetrical layouts to creative, statement-making designs. Each tile is crafted with high-quality materials, ensuring durability, stain resistance, and easy maintenance. Perfect for floors, walls, and feature areas, these tiles seamlessly fit together for a cohesive and professional finish. The modular system makes installation quick and precise, while the contemporary patterns elevate any spacebe it modern, industrial, or classic.','Beige','Contemporary, Industrial, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/121f21-e0c0-f428-56cb-c58f87e060be/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1a633c2-c5ad-1751-073-62d8e02e3b40/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4d71a0-42a4-e80-1e36-0342210dcd7c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/aee0c7-50e4-2ef4-c3c7-ee26cd21e5a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/db6bba8-2482-f4f8-b074-e4eee258fd8f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/dfc150e-e3ea-c4c8-453d-404e6ca7bac/1200x