(399,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Beige Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Beige Floor and Wall Tile Code36970 (600x1200mm, Matt)',105,'The 600x1200mm vitrified floor and wall tile is a perfect blend of modern design, durability, and refined elegance, crafted to enhance both residential and commercial spaces. Its rectangular large-format size creates a visually expansive surface by reducing grout lines, resulting in a seamless and sophisticated finish. This tile offers a premium look that complements contemporary, minimalist, and luxury interior themes while adding a sense of depth and openness to any area. Manufactured using advanced vitrification technology, the tile features high density, low water absorption, and excellent resistance to stains, scratches, and daily wear. Suitable for both floor and wall applications, it is ideal for living rooms, bedrooms, kitchens, bathrooms, corridors, offices, showrooms, and hospitality spaces. Easy to clean and low in maintenance, the 600x1200mm vitrified tile delivers long-lasting performance with timeless aesthetic appeal, making it a reliable and stylish choice for modern architectural designs.','Beige, Red','Contemporary, Minimalist, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/22adf6-5fc5-050-5347-34ab4a4a63aa/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/22adf6-5fc5-050-5347-34ab4a4a63aa/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/310f71-15e0-bdd-cda-473f8d0ce1b0/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6ece306-2d4f-1c3f-6434-7eb87be0d2e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/83a8740-e665-615b-68d8-e1064c328fd7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b2dd54a-6337-fdb-3aff-47857ed3fb3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b855116-1