(401,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Beige Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Beige Poster Wall Tile Code37890HL (600x1200mm, Matt)',850,'This vitrified poster wall tile features beautifully crafted ethnic patterns that reflect timeless artistry and cultural elegance. The intricate motifs and ornamental detailing create a striking visual impact, making it perfect for transforming ordinary walls into statement surfaces. Designed with a premium vitrified finish, it ensures durability, easy cleaning, and resistance to stains and moisture. Ideal for living rooms, pooja spaces, corridors, hospitality interiors, and commercial feature walls, this tile brings a refined blend of tradition and contemporary design to any setting.','Beige','Contemporary, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5bdfea-2ad7-3473-070c-1435a46b7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5f45b-6853-0c8d-32e1-68808a8cec6a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7d05027-b24-dfc7-27c-1bb44b66de3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b27b47e-702-572-76c3-e74bfaa5e023/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d00b0a-fca1-2c43-51ac-bf3bf0cafe24/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/da81678-e35a-4250-d65e-f6444323aea/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/da81678-e35a-4250-d65e-f6444323aea/600x600.webp','600x1200mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-beige-poster-wall-tile-code37890hl-600x1200mm-matt'),
(402,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Beige Vitrified Tiles','Imported Beige Elevation Wall Tile Code33618 (400x620mm, Matt)',462,'Enhance the architectural appeal of your walls with our 400x620mm Imported Elevation Wall Tile. Designed to mimic the natural look of stone, brick, or rugged textures, this tile brings a rich and earthy character to both indoor and outdoor spaces. Its unique design creates a realistic 3D effect, adding depth, contrast, and personality to plain surfaces. Crafted from premium-quality materials and imported for superior aesthetics, these elevation tiles are ideal for facades, boundary walls, balcony exteriors, or feature interior walls. They offer excellent weather resistance, low maintenance, and long-lasting performance, making them a smart and stylish choice for modern construction. Give your walls a bold architectural touch with our 400x620mm Imported Elevation Wall Tile. Designed to replicate the natural aesthetics of stone, slate, or brick cladding, this tile adds unmatched depth and realism to any vertical surface. With its textured finish and handcrafted appearance, it brings a timeless, earthy feel thats perfect for enhancing exterior and interior environments alike.','Beige, Red','Brick, Modern, Natural, Plain, Slate, Textured','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/31d01-762-1cd6-fb4e-ee32b2074c3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/44e3562-b84b-87e-a3c7-fed1c06250a6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4d845a5-3f7-4c0b-1b42-0a51a311a8b/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4d845a5-3f7-4c0b-1b42-0a51a311a8b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/576f32e-44f6-1ab0-e01d-a7de6105d5c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/73d2184-eee2-24b2-ce5-254375483a4/600x600.webp, https://cor