(413,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Beige Vitrified Tiles','Imported Vitrified Tile Code17994 (310x560mm, Matt)',632,'Dressed in quaint, dainty tropical prints of bird of paradise, this collection of 10 x 10 inch imported ceramic wall tiles by MyTyles accentuates on the delectable sophistication of floral motifs. Set on a crisp white base glaze, each ceramic tile features a repetitive pattern of artisanal textures with fine, artisanal details and other outlines for a satisfying mix of modernity and serenity. Each box set features four unique designs with four unique designs to create a checkered ensemble. Available in three variations, mint, prussian blue and crema with a glossy glaze to cast an aura of sleek sheen to your interiors. The appealing combination of contrast and warmth aside, the premium glaze on these tropical ceramic tiles protects against stains, abrasion, and a host of other technical challenges and damages resulting from installation or everyday use. Further accentuating the utilitarian parameters, the utilitarian performance is accompanied by sleek looks that give your interior wall facades an instant facelift.','Blue, Mix, Red, White','Ceramic, Floral, Glossy, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/178ce7a-75be-741e-f4de-1f5de277188/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/64b74a6-4516-17ae-b58-84f538dc541/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/68cf870-b2eb-bc77-6f0-83172ea0b44d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/870bcf-5052-4f31-1bed-b03ec68137/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a46c074-03e1-4d6d-a622-f271a7820c4/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a46c074-03e1-4d6d-a622-f271a7820c4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ba