(414,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Beige Vitrified Tiles','Full Body Vitrified Tile Code17751 (600x600mm, Glossy)',78,'Line your surfaces with the graceful touch of organic finishes with this collection of 2 x 2 feet vitrified wall and floor tiles by MyTyles. With a distinguished touch from the assorted organic textures on the exceptionally sturdy body, these large-format vitrified slabs sport an intermingling of muffling and graining in chantilly on an muted backdrop. The collection is made available in four variations, peanut, crema, and ivory, and slate with the sparse use of delectable textures featured throughout to transform any surface into a work of art. With thoughtfully put together tones and textures that generate ample contrast, the immaculate use of speckles and freckles makes this collection of vitrified tiles bring vertical and horizontal installations to life. Complete with a lustrous sheen from the satin matte glaze, this collection of vitrified wall and floor tiles also demonstrates extraordinary utilitarian parameters making it the perfect for end-to-end remodels while promoting minimal maintenance and upkeep.','Ivory, Red','Full Body, Glossy, Matte, Satin, Slate, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0ec43-dff6-3481-c4be-4b161172d18/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8e6f81d-5262-3e7e-8f5-d0ef36a57f2c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b5c2c65-5ed3-65b5-e64b-25dcbcd27cf/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d03ce24-dcec-41ac-6127-bcbc2124d8/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d03ce24-dcec-41ac-6127-bcbc2124d8/600x600.webp','600x600mm','https://mytyles.com/product/full-body-vitrified-tile-code17751-600x600mm-glossy'),
(415,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Beige Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Beige Floor and Wall Tile Code37459 (600x1200mm, Matt)',75,'The 600x1200mm vitrified floor and wall tile is a perfect blend of modern design, durability, and refined elegance, crafted to enhance both residential and commercial spaces. Its rectangular large-format size creates a visually expansive surface by reducing grout lines, resulting in a seamless and sophisticated finish. This tile offers a premium look that complements contemporary, minimalist, and luxury interior themes while adding a sense of depth and openness to any area. Manufactured using advanced vitrification technology, the tile features high density, low water absorption, and excellent resistance to stains, scratches, and daily wear. Suitable for both floor and wall applications, it is ideal for living rooms, bedrooms, kitchens, bathrooms, corridors, offices, showrooms, and hospitality spaces. Easy to clean and low in maintenance, the 600x1200mm vitrified tile delivers long-lasting performance with timeless aesthetic appeal, making it a reliable and stylish choice for modern architectural designs.','Beige, Red','Contemporary, Minimalist, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/218bfe7-3a81-7a48-a06-580f163c42d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5f13327-e6a4-327e-7e31-03b060c806f1/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5f13327-e6a4-327e-7e31-03b060c806f1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6d27462-055-bfef-e31e-e8ea5a87718/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8461568-1ce3-f212-4718-23a1d5087774/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8b4ccd1-244f-2fef-bec-52dcb150d0/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b86a5e7