(416,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Beige Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Beige Floor and Wall Tile Code37221 (600x1200mm, Matt)',85,'Upgrade your spaces with the 600x1200mm Vitrified Full Body Floor and Wall Tile, a perfect combination of strength, style, and versatility. Engineered with full-body vitrification technology, this tile ensures uniform color and design throughout its thickness, making it highly resistant to wear, scratches, and chippingideal for both floors and walls in residential or commercial spaces. Its large-format dimensions create a seamless, expansive look with minimal grout lines, enhancing the sense of space and elegance in any room. The tiles polished or textured finish (depending on the design) adds sophistication while reflecting light to brighten interiors. Durable, low-maintenance, and resistant to moisture and stains, it is perfect for high-traffic areas such as living rooms, kitchens, bathrooms, offices, and retail spaces. With its timeless appeal and robust performance, this full-body vitrified tile is a premium choice for those seeking beauty, longevity, and effortless upkeep in one solution.','Beige, Light, Red','Full Body, Polished, Textured, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1af27f1-c40a-af61-222f-af5e4cf1511/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/225cbeb-0cfa-506-f0e7-54adae42a17/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/225cbeb-0cfa-506-f0e7-54adae42a17/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2831bcf-f6f6-75a4-7178-3232aa0d5aee/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/286f577-8a12-fc3f-b070-4d50c3cd3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5ad1e02-2344-1ca3-8c8-dd043d2fdd4a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c30fe75-b-dcc5-72