(438,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Blue Vitrified Tiles','Full Body Vitrified Tile Code17833 (600x1200mm, Matt)',169,'With a quadrilaterally symmetrical design, this 2 x 1 feet vitrified wall tiles by MyTyles forges sturdy, alluring and handcrafted surfaces at the fraction of the resources. With full-bodied marbled prints on a crisp white surface, the body of this double-fired vitrified tile is divided into a symmetrically arranged mix of elongated scallop shapes as a minimalistic accent all over. Blending the right amount of muted grays with metallic accents against an ivory backdrop to embellish any surface with its ultra modern, contemporary touch. Available in three variants shadow, moss and ivory, each variant blends Flexible, charismatic and sophisticated, these large format vitrified wall tiles can be used to create curated and crafted floors, intriguing wall facades, exquisite hallways and entryways without any deliberation or inhibition. Creating a wonderful display of grandeur, these triple fired vitrified tiles are designed to become a lasting companion while preserving the integrity of the surface underneath.','Gray, Ivory, Metallic, Mix, Red, White','Contemporary, Full Body, Large Format, Marble, Minimalist, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/32e76ae-8c6d-f1d2-b172-5232021fdb1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3d2dab-debe-442d-a348-d6737dbdd047/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6007fb-aa6c-1ec0-b3af-5ebff65ab2c8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a12bd67-1118-e702-7465-2511c4ccc/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c3c77d-1d7d-150c-6ea-c5f68e71bed/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ceb7523-a7d7-faf3-f11f-08eb5beda65a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.b