(440,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Blue Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code2008 (200x200mm, Matt)',300,'A modern interpretation of hydraulic cement design, this 8 x 8 inch digitally printed vitrified tile from MyTyles sets your interiors as a class apart with its strong Moroccan sensibilities. With diagonally placed encaustic motifs on all the four corners, when assembled in an end to end stacked pattern, the arcs create a compelling interlocking pattern. Available in two charming colours, the blue variation uses a soft pastel blue for the arcs and a deeper cobalt blue for the corner motifs, whereas the grey variation sports arcs in deep ash-like grey with maroon motifs. Whether used to create attractive floors in the kitchen, bathroom, balcony, or any other indoor or semi-outdoor areas or as an accent detail or a charming trim on wall installations, this Moroccan tile impresses with its sensible design. Functional with strong aesthetics, this Moroccan wall and floor tile is a unique blend of novelty and rusticity.','Blue, Grey, Maroon, Pastel','Cement, Digital, Encaustic, Modern, Printed, Rustic, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3d3746f-d68a-c215-0b6b-17da40d486f/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3d3746f-d68a-c215-0b6b-17da40d486f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/403305-abed-fabb-31f-c0b356626e18/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4b473c3-6e5c-b1f0-568f-4ae1d0c2124/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6187c5-75a-06bf-f5bf-8dc3151c1ed/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8f0758d-47b5-af85-e322-e4d1ad5d7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/f1fb5bd-4fba-6ab2-eee8-748c01c221c/600x600.webp','200x200mm','https://mytyles.com/pr