(442,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Blue Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Buddha Poster Wall Tile Code23512 (600x900mm, Glossy)',3750,'Drawing inspiration from the antiques and folklores, this 2 x 3 feet vitrified Buddha wall mural tile by MyTyles serves as an enticing element in your decor that radiates sophistication. The crisp lines alongside the modern rendition of tree of life as well as the detailing on the snow white buddha stature offsets the floral patterns to imbibe a fresh, crisp simplicity to your spaces. Featuring a combination of sharp straight and curved lines, this vitrified tile uses a vibrant palette to make your decor gleam with newfound radiance. Perfect for indoor and semi-outdoor wall facades in both residential and commercial spaces, use this mural wall tile to facilitate end-to-end remodels and transformations on small or large scale remodels whether used on its own or in conjunction with other beaders, highlighters and trims. Resilient with enhanced impervosity towards dust, grime, chips, cracks, discolouration, and other forms of everyday wear and tear, this vitrified wall tile crafts low maintenance and nevertheless elegant surfaces wherever it goes.','Light, Vibrant, White','Floral, Glossy, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/033d1c-547f-613b-f4ef-e47425c1b6c8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4ad2d-f070-0561-4887-10cf28a72bf/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/55d8e5d-46b-0857-b7d4-584773cf0c6c/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/55d8e5d-46b-0857-b7d4-584773cf0c6c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c0aa4d-bf8e-fbba-3c1-61e2650c14/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/cef18f4-b1f6-d62-122-108ea0cacb8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/