(451,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Blue Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Galloping Girl Poster Wall Tile Code35420 (1200x2400mm, Sugar)',12500,'The Vitrified Galloping Girl Poster Wall Tile is a dynamic and inspiring design that captures the spirit of freedom, strength, and youthful energy. Featuring a girl in mid-gallop, this tile portrays a sense of movement, power, and grace as the figure rides with abandon, embodying the joy of motion and the untamed beauty of nature. The image is often rendered in vivid, flowing colors, with the girl''s hair and clothing captured in mid-motion, enhancing the sense of action and fluidity. Crafted from vitrified ceramic, this tile is designed for durability and resilience, offering resistance to stains, scratches, and moisture, making it perfect for both residential and commercial spaces. The vitrified finish creates a smooth, glossy surface that brings out the fine details of the design, from the movement of the girls body to the expressive quality of her features. The combination of vibrant tonesoften earthy colors mixed with bright accentsadds a sense of life and energy to the design. The Galloping Girl motif also symbolizes independence, ambition, and movement toward ones goals, making this tile not only a decorative piece but also a source of inspiration in any interior.','Mix, Red, Vibrant','Ceramic, Decorative, Glossy, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/65e0f-1852-8be-604-25bda54dc16/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b8060e-88a8-2551-ebca-cb272d61ea/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/eda7f6-f016-fba-35db-6f8e6635c6d/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/eda7f6-f016-fba-35db-6f8e6635c6d/600x600.webp','1200x2400mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-galloping-girl-poster-wall-tile-code35420-1200x2400mm-sugar'),
