(473,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Brown Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Floor and Wall Tile Code2637 (300x1200mm, Matt)',111,'Combining an impressionistic style with a touch of modernity, this collection of 1 x 4 feet vitrified wall and floor tiles by MyTyles makes your spaces look luscious with ease and grace. Reviving the charm of stone finishes and the organic touches of beige stones. A wise choice for any busy areas, these vitrified plank tiles encapsulate the functionality of planks with the top-notch digital printing technology. Available in two variations, solid and embossed, both the variants sport similar prints and textures. However, the embossed variant is decorated with ridged, notched exteriors. Complete with the fine lustre, the textures and tones in both the variants are a curious mix of intriguing and delicate impressionism. Whether used to craft exquisite floors in the kitchen, bedroom or living room, or an accent tapestry on the walls in the entryway or balcony, this collection of vitrified wall and floor slabs always shines through. Sturdy, durable, and ageless, these vitrified slabs fit in any residential and commercial setting.','Beige, Mix','Digital, Modern, Plank, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4f1fb25-65b5-3ad0-4da-2888787b847/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5aff3e-e75c-6c1-d713-a5df346b8f81/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7a18724-8711-edf7-7e3b-0cdee21703/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7fba64e-2cab-1234-267b-c21bd4ddef/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a4017b3-78c0-54dc-73e-342484578fa/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d3be116-2ce1-e3eb-100b-f7f8e6ba48/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d3be116-