(501,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Ivory Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Nano Polished Floor and Wall Tile Code10756 (600x600mm, Glossy)',36,'Personifying the elegance associated with organic textures, this collection of 2 x 2 feet nano polished vitrified wall and floor tiles by MyTyles is inspired by modern minimalism. With an assorted mix of strips and ridges in a random, etched pattern, these double fired vitrified tiles is riddled with organic hues including honey, peanut, slate and ivory detailings all over. Bringing out an instant influx of charm, all the five variants: honey, caramel, apricot, linen, and chantilly are dressed in the continuous, full-bodied patterns with streaky dilneations mimicking the natural textures for a seamless finish. The top notch craftsmanship aided by the quality of these vitrified wall and floor tiles is designed to give your indoor and semi-outdoor remodels including everyday living areas, balconies, wall facades, and other utilitarian corners with a whiff of its cosmopolitan charm. Convenient, reliable, and resilient with a subtle sheen and a sturdy build, these large format vitrified tiles make your installations all the way more elegant while making maintenance a cakewalk.','Ivory, Mix, Red','Glossy, Large Format, Modern, Nano, Natural, Polished, Slate, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/423aa7-1b7-4bf7-024-30d1a676cb6c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b4c37f0-e760-47f2-1dc3-26f06baa463/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b4c37f0-e760-47f2-1dc3-26f06baa463/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/bdd157f-4fb-f0eb-f4b8-525573dcf27/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c45d55-5c13-a026-dbde-ca8ad4a42d66/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d461da-c8f7-181-b