(503,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Ivory Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Ivory Floor and Wall Tile Code29955 (200x200mm, Matt)',230,'This 200x200mm Vitrified Floor and Wall Tile is a high-quality, durable option designed to enhance the aesthetic and functionality of both residential and commercial spaces. Manufactured using advanced vitrification techniques, this tile offers superior strength and water resistance, making it ideal for areas with high moisture or heavy foot traffic. Vitrified tiles are made with eco-friendly materials, making them an environmentally responsible choice for your home or business.','Ivory, Red','Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/02b31ab-de28-4164-00d-464823248f42/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1d00f-4b7a-d71-da06-d51844b5f12e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/52e78be-3e83-ad77-6d11-225c42c8e2d1/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/52e78be-3e83-ad77-6d11-225c42c8e2d1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6e4518d-1a1a-b1f7-b67a-857315ca31e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/865c45b-b24-eec1-f5e7-230e8b65817/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d6b0fb5-fc3b-8584-27a6-3850dcf06ca/600x600.webp','200x200mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-ivory-floor-and-wall-tile-code29955-200x200mm-matt'),
