(505,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Ivory Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Ivory Floor and Wall Tile Code36921 (600x1200mm, Matt)',85,'This 600x1200mm vitrified floor and wall tile brings a refined, contemporary appeal to any interior with its expansive slab-like format and premium digital finish. Crafted with high-quality vitrified material, it delivers exceptional strength, low water absorption, and long-lasting performance, making it suitable for high-traffic residential and commercial areas. The large size minimizes grout lines, creating a seamless, spacious, and luxurious visual effect. Its smooth, stain-resistant and scratch-resistant surface ensures easy maintenance, while its versatile design makes it ideal for living rooms, bedrooms, kitchens, bathrooms, and feature walls. A perfect choice for anyone looking for modern elegance with durable functionality.','Ivory','Contemporary, Digital, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4f42eb-85ac-527a-5e-66684d06f14/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/68b6b4d-4ba8-14c1-0d5-4f06c6841ab5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8cb3546-ddf7-70ee-6e7a-06e1a5d7ab5a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a81bbf5-ecf-454-41cc-a113b08425cd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/bf4088a-2504-3400-ee32-040211843dc/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d603045-7636-067e-8304-e458022413b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/dce7b37-db3-511e-5a8f-6feb281413ca/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/f8ca5fb-a001-2247-0d7d-eaa16f612c/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/f8ca5fb-a001-2247-0d7d-eaa16f612c/600x600.webp','600x1200mm