(507,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Ivory Vitrified Tiles','Ceramic Tile Code19352 (200x200mm, Matt)',195,'Designed to incorporate an element of tremendous fluidity in your decor with this rustic, beautiful 8 x 8 inch ceramic subway wall tile by MyTyles presents a cohesive front for that added sophisticated. The body of this ceramic wall tile is marked by numerous large grains in snow white with a delicate orange tinted crema backdrop for extraordinary strength and stunning good looks. To facilitate the addition of a minimalistic, rustic detail to your decor, the colour combination, the faux textures and the impeccable use of contrast layers across decor styles effortlessly. Whether used to refashion a kitchen or sink backsplash, or simply leverage the gentle sheen of the satin glaze, this subway wall tile facilitates end to end indoor and semi-outdoor wall facades in residential and commercial settings alike. Complete with a sturdy build, an extraordinary satin matte glaze and intricate details, this ceramic subway tile makes for a timeless addition to any surface.','Orange, White','Ceramic, Matte, Minimalist, Rustic, Satin, Subway','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3a20c58-e6-5fbe-06d-608c348423/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3a20c58-e6-5fbe-06d-608c348423/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3a3a770-a46d-0ac5-516a-c274bd1f75a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4baf34c-67d1-635-3baa-a11c65266/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/520b7a-ceb8-0de2-bec1-fd8af68d574/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7220-2e85-7b5b-c7f1-f2ef3a1cf645/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/85f56e-7c6-612e-c4ac-463a737fe80/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.bi