(508,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Ivory Vitrified Tiles','Imported Porcelain Tile Code21487 (450x450mm, Matt)',601,'Off white speckles and stunning beige marbled grains lace the body of this sophisticated imported porcelain wall and floor tile by MyTyles. Equipped with a mesmerising textures, the influence of split face cross sections radiates through the presence of this porcelain tile. The satine matte finish coupled with the fine interplay of travertine textures shine with its sincere and heartwarming organic touch. Whether used to create an exceptional wall facade in the kitchen or shower surrounds or a fantastic flooring surface for your indoor & outdoor floors, the sophistication of this porcelain wall and floor tile offers an immediate influx of organic finess. With a low maintenance nature, exceptional abrasion resistance and exceptional durability, this imported porcelain tile makes its presence felt without overwhelming your senses.','Beige, White','Marble, Matte, Porcelain, Satin','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/00346b6-57ba-5617-17e6-ba6055eaef06/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/128e2e-228c-a66d-7a14-6f7eee738e07/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/70ccb4-ed7a-5ad-242-c4dbc5c42d4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/77aa0e-3cc5-1087-307-3d584e1ab123/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a3463a3-107f-b16a-1dc4-11d60edb5c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b050d-247a-8cb3-c5f6-adb2e5847e/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b050d-247a-8cb3-c5f6-adb2e5847e/600x600.webp','450x450mm','https://mytyles.com/product/imported-porcelain-tile-code21487-450x450mm-matt'),
(509,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Ivory Vitrified Tiles','Ceramic Floor and Wall Tile Code3899 (300x300mm,Matt)',65,'This collection 12 x 12 inch ceramic wall and floor tiles by MyTyles impresses with its superb contrast and thereby raving compliments from the first glance. The sturdy body of each glazed ceramic tile is decorated with numerous offset and unpredicatble split face textures in muted hues all over. Generously tesselated with the strikingly stunning veining coupled with the undeniable seamlessness creates the illusion of natural stones with extreme humility. Available in an assorted mix of muted hues, the collection displays breathtaking intricacy and capitalizes on top-notch digital prints for its inherent sophistication Perfect for a wide spectrum of indoor and semi-outdoor remodels, these ceramic wall and floor tiles blend seamlessly across a variety of decor styles to craft delectable front porches, foyer areas, corridors, entryways, hallways, balconies, or any other nooks and crannies. The sturdy build couples with the ease of installation and maintenance of these large format ceramic tiles is perfect for those overlooked surfaces that crave a touch of contemporary glamor.','Mix, Red','Ceramic, Contemporary, Digital, Glazed, Large Format, Natural','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4638c5b-f36f-442-22f7-86a047bf31a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/81d373-0127-e8c6-11c3-83c65fc4e2b6/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/81d373-0127-e8c6-11c3-83c65fc4e2b6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b72cca7-5a4c-c2e2-ef22-78e13a07fd50/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c8107ce-57a4-368f-13e8-0ea76bfedc2/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/fc6171d-ddc-53f-b430-84664380181c/600x600.webp','