(511,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Ivory Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Ivory Digital Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code36574 (400x400mm, Matt)',59,'The 400x400mm vitrified parking floor and wall tile is specially designed to withstand heavy load, constant movement, and harsh outdoor conditions. Manufactured using high-density vitrification technology, this tile offers excellent strength, low water absorption, and superior resistance to stains, impact, and abrasion. Its compact size ensures better grip and stability, making it ideal for parking areas, driveways, ramps, basements, and utility zones. The durable surface finish provides enhanced slip resistance for safety, while the robust structure ensures long-lasting performance with minimal maintenance. Suitable for both floor and wall applications, this 400x400mm vitrified parking tile combines functionality, reliability, and a clean, structured look for residential and commercial exteriors.','Ivory, Red','Digital, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/06b5041-3f81-565e-f053-3fd8ae2f5c3f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/11662-1fa1-cbce-d3b7-82ec0370c6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/23d36f8-02d3-ea62-3484-1f44df4231d4/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/23d36f8-02d3-ea62-3484-1f44df4231d4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/32c8d17-85d-221c-0c88-0cba7267b24/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b341860-af1c-e7e4-30e5-f2f76fedc2/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ce54c74-025e-5c2d-b417-6a6bba776f3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/efd8c6-7db4-75a-832-05c31c1a3e6d/600x600.webp','400x400mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-ivory-digital-parking-floor-and-wall-tile-code36574-400x400mm-matt'),
(512,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Ivory Vitrified Tiles','Double Charged Vitrified Tile Code23973 (600x600mm, Glossy)',43,'Earthy hues meet split face textures in this collection of 2 x 2 feet vitrified digitally printed parking tiles by MyTyles. Set on a stoic, neutral, muted base glaze, numerous grains and freckles impart an organic finesse akin to the look and feel of water percolating down the sand whereas the use of tones on these double fired vitrified tiles introduces a sense of seamlessness to your design. Offering muffling and distressed finishes with the gentle tessellations, this collection of vitrified wall and floor tiles are made available in eight exclusive colors in sand, ash, peanut, shadow, sienna, smoke and taupe to elevate the look and feel of your spaces with its awe-inducing looks. Timeless with the sturdy build, the exteriors of this satin matte double fired vitrified parking tile renders itself as an undeniable choice for both outdoor and semi-outdoor remodels in residential and commercial spaces. The impeccable sense of style of these large format vitrified tiles coupled with the utilitarian functionalities resulting in minimal maintenance and upkeep make it a resilient choice.','Red','Digital, Distressed, Double Charge, Glossy, Large Format, Matte, Printed, Satin, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0d31747-ccdb-36f5-dfd-c8a1cbd2404/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/20d4a20-553-808-174a-dcd1c5b8a74b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/31a126-66b1-40a-3f3b-1dfd46fc5e68/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/44666ef-010-2a1b-343d-dc2571f0df1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/68105-8868-448-cd4a-17d04bee2a/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ac17b0-1a8f-a35-10ce-2