(532,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Red With Green Red Cherry Poster Wall Tile Code32370 (600x1200mm, Glossy, 4Pcs)',10500,'A Vitrified Poster Wall Tile is a stylish and functional wall tile designed to replicate the look and feel of a large poster or mural. These tiles often feature high-resolution images or artistic designs that can transform a wall into a statement piece. The vitrified aspect refers to the tile''s manufacturing process, where ceramic materials are fired at high temperatures, making the tile highly durable, non-porous, and resistant to stains, scratches, and moisture.','Green, Red','Artistic, Ceramic, Glossy, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0161f5-a25-6741-235-d34ace6473/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0161f5-a25-6741-235-d34ace6473/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/126e6c-a757-72a1-e3ae-e22c7acd55/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1a4a6ed-60f8-7ff-7e77-ad37f2050d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1fab422-058e-2a22-cda4-6846a32bf85/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/24144d8-dd37-f573-3f1a-414551b35780/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4d71f8-ad55-14ce-8282-54b2458875e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6e057a3-0565-2ede-62af-0cab8a745b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8e8362c-c823-8012-b7d2-2108cca57f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d56d71-5a38-2b52-a3fa-b11f6876a6b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/eb5dfd8-82f7-38d5-5c47-4f7ec3a1687/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/stor