(534,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Carpet Rangoli Vitrified Tiles Code22124 (4x6Feet, Glossy)',16800,'A chic combination of neutral hues and organic warmth, this 2 x 4 feet sandstone mural wall tile by MyTyles is refined yet simple. The sturdy and chiseled body of this mural tile is laced with detailed embossing and etched detailing that matches the contemporary effortless affair while giving your installations a splendid, intricately assembled look. The CNC-cut motifs on the sandstone teakwood blocks are simplistic yet detailed while lending a mid-century European aesthetic. Pouring a limitless stream of warmth, the mosaic grid layout is flexible and brings a stellar artisanal quality to your home. Design alluring accent walls in indoor (living room, bedroom, dining rooms, and other indoor wall panels), outdoor (garden, balcony, exteriors of your residential or commercial properties,) and semi-outdoor (verandas, courtyards, entryways, hallways, foyer areas, lobbies, and more) settings with this sandstone mural tile. Accentuating on textures with demure contrast, these large format stone slabs impart a stunning look to your remodels.','','Contemporary, Glossy, Large Format, Mosaic, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/13a6cf-266b-2030-8ef5-346ddcbe0cc3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2ccc6da-a564-72b6-f6d-deffb18ca5fd/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2ccc6da-a564-72b6-f6d-deffb18ca5fd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7ba04e-ccee-054e-e1c3-4db11ed3eb1/600x600.webp','4x6Feet','https://mytyles.com/product/carpet-rangoli-vitrified-tiles-code22124-4x6feet-glossy'),
(535,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Imported Carpet Rangoli Tile Code21518 (600x600m, Glossy)',2800,'Riveting with a sophisticated geometric exterior, this 4 x 4 feet vitrified carpet floor tile by MyTyles establishes an elegant feat to your decor. The box set of four carpet tiles consists of a circular motif against a chantilly base glaze with garnet and goldenrod details including arcs, loops and numerous other floral decorations that lace the body of this vitrified tile into symmetrical halves in shades of beige and ash. The contrast and the soothing organic touch mesmerizes from the get go. A tranquil combination of vibrant colors and glossy finishes radiate an aura of elegance around your indoor and semi-outdoor installations with its visual appeal. Complete with a glossy glaze that protects against mechanical damages as well as premature wear and tear, this large format carpet tile delivers sophisticated transformations without any aesthetic or technological hassles.','Beige, Gold, Vibrant','Floral, Geometric, Glossy, Large Format, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/10bff8e-40a1-0eb1-d7ff-1ce4072fc/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1a2fb3b-721-a80f-c45f-d2b4e0b31ac/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2433e5f-7cd2-ae0-d4af-45fff55403/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/384660c-a28e-61e2-ba61-5ee6be3ec4e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/532b226-4d48-2427-e6ee-24b1fb7ae70/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/70a42b1-31a-8d74-b434-2424d5dc44/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/74d2cd8-8512-0261-7ec3-708122cc7e42/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e464df1-5