(536,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Imported Carpet Rangoli Tile Code21514 (600x600m, Glossy)',2800,'Displaying a delectable blend of ethnic palette and eclectic style, this collection of 2 x 2 feet vitrified carpet floor tiles by MyTyles seeks to impart a strong style statement to your remodels. With a thick border, a regal tone and numerous ethnic accents decorate the body of these large-format vitrified tiles. Sporting a steady, inclusive design while exuding a bespoke contemporary flair, the contrast and patterns liases well with a variety of decor styles. Both the variants electric blue and garnet are an enthralling combination of goldenrod yellows and pincushion frames with a multitude of muffling, the overall design exudes a sophisticated medley of charming ethnic vibes. Brightening and uplifting, this carpet floor tiles uplifts spirits with its inherent ability to deliver profound transformations with its exceptional good looks. Impervious to discoloration, cracks, and everyday wear and tear, the minimal upkeep and maintenance of these double fired vitrified tiles coordinates well with its resilience to deliver swift and delectable remodels.','Blue, Gold, Red, Yellow','Contemporary, Glossy, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/005bc7-1373-2355-c3d-a5fec6fe17c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/40d6856-e676-2722-c321-8e2b83a5a704/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6f4fdb7-40d0-ef8-d353-780085e207f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/78cdac1-4cb-edea-ed5d-ed650e4ecc/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a4b2ecc-bab5-dfee-1585-e6186affaf38/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/aed7040-6322-e880-0f7e-f7480d61b13/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.b