(537,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Border Tile Code17080 (45x600mm, Metallic)',200,'With a velvety warm beige backdrop, this collection 1.5 x 12 inch metallic border wall tile by MyTyles capitalizes on duotone textures for a flush, contemporary touch. The combination of embossed prints and consistent textures create an illusion of intricate, authentic ornamentation that is consistent with the theme of the border tiles. The tactile and printed undulations bring exquisite contrast while the palette encourages an influx of timeless class to your surfaces. Compatible with a host of decor styles, organic finishes and an array of accessories, the collection features three assorted shades including carmine, chantilly and gold that introduces subtle movement into the space. The lustrous sheen on these ceramic border tiles beautifies an assortment of surfaces while on the utilitarian front, it imparts a generous amount of contrast to your indoor and semi-outdoor devotional areas. Low on maintenance and unbelievably good looking, these ceramic wall tiles are a hardwearing means to introduce class and elegance to your residential and commercial remodels.','Beige, Gold, Metallic','Ceramic, Contemporary, Printed, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/20dac6a-1c24-4bbc-f3b4-61b6b5ae7bfd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4ecc102-3d08-e074-0afa-f1d3b52422d6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4ed550f-47-68bd-865-17cf073a3bc/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/af6806a-7f2-418a-f16b-bec72e623/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b02eba-ff6c-5510-ace1-748024d554/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b1e5dbd-0c0e-8a4a-a6e6-77b17858d52/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles