(540,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Imported Red Vitrified Floor and Wall Tile Code28842 (600x600mm, Matt)',189,'Upgrade your floors and walls with 2x2 feet imported vitrified tiles in a matte finish. Designed for both style and durability, these tiles feature a smooth, non-reflective surface that adds a modern, understated elegance to any room. Their vitrified construction ensures strength, making them resistant to stains, scratches, and moisture, making them ideal for high-traffic areas in both residential and commercial settings. The large 2x2 feet format reduces grout lines, providing a seamless, expansive look perfect for living rooms, offices, and lobbies. Easy to maintain and highly durable, these matte finish tiles are the perfect solution for spaces that require both aesthetics and long-lasting performance.','Red','Matte, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2c5f8ea-e4ee-354f-0f77-5dd07bdca34e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5a0ad6d-ede7-7ba2-40fb-254535886dff/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/71baf3-6bb1-60fd-8c36-412231230d01/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/72eb6e-7ac2-2f4a-5d3-52a150cc7cd/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a44ed5-0a3-bbc2-023a-5fedd6825e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d2df3-26e-b01-ae67-7b8d8046c337/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d2df3-26e-b01-ae67-7b8d8046c337/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ef4127d-1fac-e4f3-d83d-85bf318d8772/600x600.webp','600x600mm','https://mytyles.com/product/imported-red-vitrified-floor-and-wall-tile-code28842-600x600mm-matt'),
(541,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Carpet Rangoli Vitrified Tiles Code22120 (4x6Feet, Glossy)',16800,'A chic combination of neutral hues and organic warmth, this 2 x 4 feet sandstone mural wall tile by MyTyles is refined yet simple. The sturdy and chiseled body of this mural tile is laced with detailed embossing and etched detailing that matches the contemporary effortless affair while giving your installations a splendid, intricately assembled look. The CNC-cut motifs on the sandstone teakwood blocks are simplistic yet detailed while lending a mid-century European aesthetic. Pouring a limitless stream of warmth, the mosaic grid layout is flexible and brings a stellar artisanal quality to your home. Design alluring accent walls in indoor (living room, bedroom, dining rooms, and other indoor wall panels), outdoor (garden, balcony, exteriors of your residential or commercial properties,) and semi-outdoor (verandas, courtyards, entryways, hallways, foyer areas, lobbies, and more) settings with this sandstone mural tile. Accentuating on textures with demure contrast, these large format stone slabs impart a stunning look to your remodels.','','Contemporary, Glossy, Large Format, Mosaic, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/011f55-c6f-8eac-e80-7b66ac43a811/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/011f55-c6f-8eac-e80-7b66ac43a811/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2e137-11a4-624-601e-6bca85614552/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2e6dc5-d177-e31-5fb3-8b5ae62f4ece/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7163bc7-47c-bb50-100-347251b117ae/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a314807-0506-b4e7-0c5b-754fa25c52bf/600x600.webp','4x6Feet','https://mytyles.com/product/carpet-rangoli-vitri