(547,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Red Terrazzo Floor and Wall Tile Code32519 (600x1200mm, Matt)',131,'Elevate your interiors with the timeless charm of our 600x1200mm Vitrified Terrazzo Floor and Wall Tile. Crafted with precision and durability in mind, this tile brings the classic appeal of terrazzo into a modern, large-format design. Its vitrified body ensures exceptional strength, low porosity, and resistance to stains and moisture, making it ideal for both residential and commercial applications. The terrazzo pattern features a dynamic blend of aggregates, offering a unique, speckled look that adds character to any space. Whether used on floors or walls, it delivers a seamless, contemporary aesthetic with minimal grout lines. Perfect for living rooms, kitchens, bathrooms, lobbies, or feature walls.','Red','Contemporary, Modern, Terrazzo, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/16d53f-4aa0-d85d-1443-21eccc5ab7fa/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/17baaf1-be1c-2d2e-0688-f3362caa73c2/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/28bafa8-4c-bbc3-8a3a-6373567c2c8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4f8204-1d4-246d-455-ac8d71b6d8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5d488-45af-c650-6d53-c1ec7602216/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/61361e-4034-4248-2df-cdf3a3741a8/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/61361e-4034-4248-2df-cdf3a3741a8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6b41f-5ec3-4014-bf-e5373516e11b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6bf14c-5f1a-f136-8e42-1cfa2eb6a87/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod