(552,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Red Moroccan Floor and Wall Tile Code33441 (600x600mm, Sugar)',112,'A 600x600mm Vitrified Moroccan Tile is a stylish and high-quality tile designed to add a touch of elegance and cultural charm to any space. These tiles are part of the vitrified category, meaning they are fired at high temperatures to create a dense, non-porous surface, ensuring durability and ease of maintenance. The vitrification process makes these tiles incredibly strong, highly resistant to stains, scratches, and water absorption. This makes them perfect for both residential and commercial applications. he Moroccan design on these tiles brings a timeless and exotic appeal, with geometric patterns, bold colors, and artistic motifs that make them stand out. They work particularly well in creating focal points or adding character to contemporary, traditional, or even eclectic interiors.','Red','Artistic, Contemporary, Geometric, Traditional, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/257e65d-4c0-5850-cca4-b0d173388d/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/257e65d-4c0-5850-cca4-b0d173388d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3bb8d0-1ebe-46c0-a065-3cbb2ec416d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3f40f6a-5a06-3fae-2a67-330185f66553/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/6bafe70-81d-fbb-4515-d8a7e66aed/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7f7b7f8-5f67-a801-1416-5327c6db86e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7ffdf5-eda6-3754-043d-1d0484ce6e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/b4cba7f-31d2-12e-a52c-d4e2084dbf7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/pr