(553,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Red and White Tree Mosaic Wall Tile Code35411 (4x8 Feet, Sugar)',12500,'The Vitrified Red Crimson Rose Mosaic Wall Tile is a luxurious and passionate statement piece that captures the timeless beauty of roses in full bloom. Featuring rich crimson roses rendered in intricate mosaic detail, it evokes elegance, romance, and artistic sophistication. The vibrant red hues create a striking visual impact, while the mosaic texture adds depth, dimension, and a dynamic play of light across the surface. Crafted from premium vitrified material, this tile ensures exceptional durability, stain resistance, and a flawless finish that preserves its brilliance over time. The intricate mosaic artistry allows each rose to stand out as a focal point, transforming ordinary walls into captivating feature spaces. Ideal for feature walls, bedrooms, living rooms, lobbies, boutique showrooms, luxury restaurants, and hotel interiors, this mural elevates spaces with bold elegance and timeless charm. Its rich, passionate color palette pairs beautifully with modern, classic, or opulent décor, creating a luxurious and inviting ambiance. The Red Crimson Rose Mosaic Wall Tile is more than a wall coveringit is a celebration of romance, artistry, and sophistication, designed for interiors that demand both beauty and impact.','Crimson, Light, Red, Vibrant, White','Artistic, Modern, Mosaic, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1210de-4421-2320-ee80-46af57ab5853/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2a3e083-d8e6-4a03-ceb4-7b023b54636/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/2a3e083-d8e6-4a03-ceb4-7b023b54636/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5af0f83-5d8-f1a-045-44ed3ec67cbf/600x600.webp','4x8','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-red-and-white-tree-mosaic-wall-tile-code35411-4x8-feet-sugar'),
(554,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code23038 (300x300mm, Metallic)',355,'Displaying the simplicity of Tastir and its geometric essence, this collection of 12 x 12 inch Moroccan wall and floor tiles by MyTyles creates a remarkable first impression. The smart use of grains and speckles ensure maximum contrast, making small areas look larger and sizeable areas look cohesively cozy and well put together. With a a simplistic pattern and a medley of charming contrasting hues, this collection of double fired vitrified tiles do not overpower any other elements of the decor. The blue variation combines teal with prussian blue whereas the red variant combines olive with reddish sienna tones; both highlighted with golden accents all over. Use this vitrified wall and floor tile to design exquisite installations in the kitchen, bathroom, mudrooms, front porches, living rooms, balconies or bedrooms either as an accent or as a full blown repetitive body. With a sizeable design, rectified edges, and the subtle sheen from the satin matte glaze, this Moroccan tile displays a sense of effortlessness and timelessness that illuminates your entire space without any overwhelm.','Blue, Gold, Light, Metallic, Olive, Red, Teal','Geometric, Matte, Satin, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/3a4a30f-4b5-358e-c6f7-5802ba04cea/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/431e04a-f124-0ae8-6b6e-28f1c58e44/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/70cbee5-5325-c8ff-f8a5-32ab35b3668c/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/78f4fd7-f5a3-b21e-63-be312736f5f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7bffa71-f836-0e8-1f81-b807cf8ff7e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/aefda53-1d06-73f7-580-cb33e5fcfa/120