(555,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Imported Red Subway Wall Tile Code37782 (70x216mm, Glossy)',555,'The 70x216mm Imported Subway Wall Tile offers a sleek, elongated format that adds a modern twist to the classic subway style. Perfect for kitchen backsplashes, bathroom walls, and feature areas, this tile creates a clean and stylish look with its smooth finish and refined edges. The extended size enhances visual depth and allows versatile layouts such as brick bond, vertical stack, or herringbone patterns. Crafted from premium imported material, it ensures durability, easy maintenance, and long-lasting elegance making it an ideal choice for both contemporary and timeless interior spaces.','Red','Brick, Contemporary, Glossy, Herringbone, Modern, Subway','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1e663ab-bea5-845f-7d0c-2d5c831c078b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4da273a-4ace-b3e0-42de-c265c5d332d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4e6242a-6cf8-2a3c-d1ef-3383b7717a6/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4e6242a-6cf8-2a3c-d1ef-3383b7717a6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/747fe4-a8ff-37f6-12ee-ae3d6de65fb1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/afae45-541-a21-873-4567e62e487/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ba36ed-bba-f853-61b-fdba773aa0b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c0ee31-2a50-a0fa-11fe-d1e18aa70034/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/cd635c7-50af-2d37-1a15-1ea226cdc3b5/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e07b13f-5de6-6f64-5433-11b15b8f6/600x600.webp','70x216mm','https://mytyles.com/pr