(558,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code3330 (300x300mm, Matt)',235,'Add vigour to your interiors with this vitrified wall and floor tile from MyTyles. A riot of colours, this Moroccan tile evokes eclectic vibrance into any surface with its appealing use of loud colours and interesting placement. Measuring 12 X 12 inches, each vitrified tile in this series is divided into four asymmetrical quadrants. With a bold polygonal shape and a matte finish, it is an ideal choice for the living room, bedroom, kitchen, bathroom, shower, balcony, and terrace floor. Use it to create an authentic wall installation on an accent wall or decorate utilitarian areas like kitchen backsplashes, sink backsplashes, powder room, or mudroom. Created with toxin-free and allergen-free raw materials and formaldehyde and VOC-free glazes, it blends in kid-friendly and pet-friendly households and commercial environments with ease. Impervious to most common forms of wear and tear, like discolouration and abrasion, the matte finish makes it low maintenance and high on resistance.','','Cement, Matte, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4531eb4-0003-f7cc-4e3d-53b1d220d207/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5de85e-2e30-80b7-0124-c43b12f88d6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ba8063-4bb1-2782-fdd4-bab4cdab6d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d532af5-508d-d31-648e-ef017bdda63/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d532af5-508d-d31-648e-ef017bdda63/600x600.webp','300x300mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-moroccan-tile-code3330-300x300mm-matt'),
(559,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Red Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Moroccan Tile Code18961 (300x300mm, Matt)',244,'A remarkable blend of modern neutrals against an ivory backdrop, this collection of 12 x 12 inch Moroccan wall and floor tiles by MyTyles radiates earthy fervour from the get go. Embellished with uninterrupted, fluid, thick stripes forming an encaustic pattern, the sturdy body of these double fired vitrified tiles oozes with undeniable charm. Available in two variants, olive and terracotta, both the variants are incredibly delectable in their own right while forging charming, sinfully irresistible spaces. An incredible mix of luxurious textures, a stunning digital print, and other utilitarian parameters, use this vitrified wall and flor tile for transcending vertical and horizontal surfaces into something ethereal. Attributing to rectified edges, repetitive patterns, and sizeable design, these Moroccan tiles lend a classy finish for breathtaking indoor or semi-outdoor accent features.','Ivory, Mix, Olive, Red, Terracotta','Digital, Encaustic, Modern, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5eec71a-8751-eeca-6233-722d628c401/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/7f48eb8-4d2b-82c2-cbf6-ee5600583a6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8d05fb-06c8-7b67-0844-e3db3e1d088/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8d05fb-06c8-7b67-0844-e3db3e1d088/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/aacf68f-6431-fd1-747a-a30ce0d75540/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/af5bdec-2cc-88d-035-e74e64c3b6ec/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c30a6b7-f748-6d87-4721-76a4dd2a7dd/600x600.webp','300x300mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-moroccan-tile-code18961-300x3