(591,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Cream Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Cream Elevation Wall Tile Code8033 (300x600mm, Matt)',75,'A humble juxtaposition of stone textures and running brick layout, this vitrified elevation wall tile by MyTyles uses a 3D design to add a layer of intricate, vintage aesthetic to your redesign. Alternating between long and shorter brick like patterns, the fine replication of the stone textures is truly remarkable. The faux grout lines add slight grooves, and ridges facilitate a coarse texture to the matte surface which adds an element of functionality and sophistication to your wall installations. Remodel your entryways, hallways, foyer areas, living rooms, bedrooms, mudrooms, balconies, or the exterior of your house with this vitrified tile. The 2 x 1 feet vitrified body facilitates easy installation, simple levelling, and helps in achieving a seamless one-piece effect with ease. A major portion of the convenience on the installation and maintenance front for this elevation wall tile can be attributed to the rectified edges. Low on maintenance and high on tenacity, this elevation tile ages gracefully with your home.','Cream, Light, Red','Brick, Matte, Vintage, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/0f4512-0a1c-0b8e-817e-84d735b31d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1353271-a0a6-c161-c68d-ecb40a18b1b0/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/1353271-a0a6-c161-c68d-ecb40a18b1b0/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/251a7d-1068-226a-33f4-b1287d42f572/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4a3e64a-857-7cd7-6f6-3c223f510f8/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/5041bb-d423-dd6e-65df-6c0a37b4ec/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/602