(592,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Cream Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Beige Floor and Wall Tile Code33777 (600x1200mm, Matt)',93,'Cream surfaces set a neutral, welcoming tone that works across many interior schemes, and this vitrified cream floor and wall tile blends that aesthetic with dependable performance. Identified as Code33777, it comes in a 600x1200 mm format with a matt surface that softens reflections while enhancing depth and cohesion. The vitrified body is manufactured with a balanced thickness of 8 mm designed to support both foot traffic performance and stable vertical use, making it suitable for varied interior elevations. The matt finish spreads light gently over the surface and helps conceal minor marks without sacrificing overall brightness. Its streamlined profile complements muted palettes, stone textures, timber details and muted metal trims, making styling options flexible. Because the format is generous, grout lines become minimal, allowing the cream surface to feel more continuous and less visually segmented. This size also reduces pattern break, helping floors feel unified and walls appear calmer. Combined with thoughtful lighting and consistent grout choice, the tile brings understated elegance and everyday reliability. Whether it is applied across floors or walls, this tile creates spaces that feel balanced, coherent, and curated.','Beige, Cream, Light, Red','Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/10bc08-806f-cafb-3b56-be5efd5c7ad0/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/71783da-eaf3-134-123b-aead6355adc/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/855bc-04c-22d4-1c16-6c5e7d46dbd2/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a0fed3a-5dca-8cc0-65f5-0b0303556df3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a42742c-bbd3-4742-87cb-50f7ce5d8fcf/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/a82261a-cead-3e1-71af-457cd7c06b3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/af35bf7-c30-643a-1b4e-bb316ad6e01e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d55420-7b8-aea0-a158-807f4205b44d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/fecda51-a7c1-86d5-0c4e-0571ce3741b6/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/fecda51-a7c1-86d5-0c4e-0571ce3741b6/600x600.webp','600x1200mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-cream-floor-and-wall-tile-code33777-600x1200mm-matt'),
(593,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles / Cream Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Cream Moroccan Floor and Wall Tile Code29977 (200x200mm, Matt)',230,'This 200x200mm Moroccan Floor and Wall Tile brings a touch of exotic charm and intricate artistry to any space. Known for its bold, geometric patterns and vibrant colors, it features traditional Moroccan designs that can be used to create a striking focal point in kitchens, bathrooms, living rooms, or entryways. Whether used on floors or walls, these tiles offer durability and a unique aesthetic that can enhance modern or classic interiors alike. Made from high-quality ceramic or cement, they are easy to maintain and offer a long-lasting finish. With their distinct, hand-crafted appearance, these tiles infuse your home with a sense of warmth and cultural elegance, ideal for both residential and commercial applications.','Cream, Vibrant','Cement, Ceramic, Geometric, Modern, Traditional, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/543cfc3-fa5-e4ec-c13-432228f7/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/543cfc3-fa5-e4ec-c13-432228f7/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/82f53-1ae5-46f-76a1-dec78cf8ea31/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/88071-77d6-71d4-db6c-2ac8e417d65/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/c46482e-dd66-473-0edf-7ebbb46f52b/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/f2a634-4c0c-dd4b-b308-5bb12b28b0e/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/ff74671-fc11-3a30-7d71-e586f6d407fb/600x600.webp','200x200mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-cream-moroccan-floor-and-wall-tile-code29977-200x200mm-matt'),
