(598,'Tiles / Vitrified Tiles','Vitrified Brown Digital Parking Floor and Wall Tile Code29672 (500x500mm, Matt)',66,'This 20x20 inch digital parking tile is engineered to withstand heavy traffic, both from vehicles and pedestrians. It features a high-definition, digitally printed surface that allows for intricate, customizable patterns or designs. The tile is typically made from materials like porcelain, ceramic, or high-density composite, which ensures strength, longevity, and resistance to wear and tear.','Brown, Red','Ceramic, Digital, Porcelain, Printed, Vitrified','https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/233e6bb-7a16-a70d-5222-1fdb1e1566a6/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/42058e4-d600-3521-0cbe-ef00471684f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/4841bc7-4682-d30d-ab3-6300b57e5b8f/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/80df5d2-8071-77e-5f06-011b8bdb5cb1/1200x1200.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/80df5d2-8071-77e-5f06-011b8bdb5cb1/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/8c6ecd-b765-f427-1815-7d35c5ca32d/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/d66737-dc14-0bc4-487-3bcdef12ece4/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/db508d-2fee-2cfa-db7-dfbcf8a63b3/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/e67e564-8188-856d-8e1-7872533e7712/600x600.webp, https://corewebimage1.mytyles.biz/storage/prod/public/products/images/f8e18b-d1f-505c-d500-35d6ae345d4c/600x600.webp','500x500mm','https://mytyles.com/product/vitrified-brown-digital-parking-floor-and-wall-tile-code29672-500x500mm-matt'),
